var book = {
	"name": "1 Khronikl",
	"numChapters": 29,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> U Adam, u Seth, u Enosh;",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> u Kenan, u Mahalalil, u Jared;",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> u Enokh, u Methuselah, u Lamekh:",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> u Noah, u Shem, u Ham, bad u Japheth.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ki khun shynrang u Japheth: u Gomer, bad u Magog, bad u Madai, bad u Jaban, bad u Tubal, bad u Meshekh, bad u Tiras.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Gomer: u Ashkenas, bad u Diphath, bad u Togarmah.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Jaban: u Elishah, bad u Tarshish, u Kittim, bad u Rodanim.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ki khun shynrang u Ham: u Kush, bad u Misraim, u Put, bad u Kanaan.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Kush: u Seba, bad u Habilah, bad u Sabta, bad u Raamah, bad u Sabteka. Bad ki khun shynrang u Raamah: u Sheba, bad u Dedan.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad u Kush u la pynkha ïa u Nimrod; une u la sdang ban long uba khraw bor ha ka khyndew.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad u Misraim u la pynkha ïa ki Lud, bad ïa ki Anam, bad ïa ki Lehab, bad ïa ki Naphtuh,",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> bad ïa ki Pathrus, bad ïa ki Kasluh (na kiba la wan mih ki Philistia), bad ïa ki Kaphtor.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad u Kanaan u la pynkha ïa u Sidon, u khun nyngkong jong u, bad u Heth;",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> bad ïa ki Jebus, bad ïa ki Amor, bad ïa ki Girgash;",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> bad ïa ki Hib, bad ïa ki Ark, bad ïa ki Sin;",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> bad ïa ki Arbad, bad ïa ki Semar, bad ïa ki Hamath.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ki khun shynrang u Shem: u Elam, bad u Asshur, bad u Arpakhshad, bad u Lud, bad u Aram, bad u Us, bad u Hul, bad u Gether, bad u Meshekh.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad u Arpakhshad u la pynkha ïa u Shelah, bad u Shelah u la pynkha ïa u Eber.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad ha u Eber la kha ar ngut ki khun shynrang: ka kyrteng uwei, “u Peleg”; naba ha ki sngi jong u la pynïabynta ïa ka khyndew; bad ka kyrteng u para jong u, “u Joktan”.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad u Joktan u la pynkha ïa u Almodad, bad u Sheleph, bad u Hasarmabeth, bad u Jerah;",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> bad u Hadoram, bad u Usal, bad u Diklah;",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> bad u Ebal, bad u Abimael, bad u Sheba;",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> bad u Ophir, bad u Habilah, bad u Jobab. Kine baroh ki la long ki khun shynrang u Joktan.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> U Shem, u Arpakhshad, u Shelah;",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> u Eber, u Peleg, u Rew,",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> u Serug, u Nahor, u Terah;",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> u Abram (uta u long u Abraham).",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Ki khun shynrang u Abraham: u Isaak, bad u Ishmael.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Kine ki long ki jingkha pateng jong ki: u khun nyngkong jong u Ishmael, u Nebaioth; hadien kata, u Kedar, bad u Abdil, bad u Mibsam,",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> u Mishma, bad u Dumah, u Massa, u Hadad, u Tema,",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> u Jetur, u Naphish, bad u Kedemah. Kine ki long ki khun shynrang u Ishmael.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang ka Keturah, ka tnga kliar u Abraham: ka la kha ïa u Simran, bad ïa u Jokshan, bad ïa u Medan, bad ïa u Midian, bad ïa u Ishbak, bad ïa u Shuah. Bad ki khun shynrang u Jokshan: u Sheba, bad u Dedan.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Midian: u Ephah, bad u Epher, bad u Hanokh, bad u Abida, bad u Eldaah. Kine baroh ki la long ki khun shynrang ka Keturah.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Bad u Abraham u la pynkha ïa u Isaak. Ki khun shynrang u Isaak: u Iso, bad u Israel.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Ki khun shynrang u Iso: u Eliphas, u Reuel, bad u Jeush, bad u Jalam, bad u Korah.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Ki khun shynrang u Eliphas: u Teman, bad u Omar, u Sephi, bad u Gatam, u Kenas, bad u Timna, bad u Amalek.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Ki khun shynrang u Reuel: u Nahath, u Serah, u Shammah, bad u Missah.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Seir: u Lotan bad u Shobal bad u Sibeon bad u Anah, bad u Dishon bad u Eser bad u Dishan.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Lotan: u Hori bad u Homam; bad ka Timna ka la long ka para u Lotan.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Ki khun shynrang u Shobal: u Alian bad u Manahath bad u Ebal, u Shephi bad u Onam. Bad ki khun shynrang u Sibeon: u Aïah bad u Anah.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Ki khun shynrang u Anah: u Dishon. Bad ki khun shynrang u Dishon: u Hamran bad u Eshban bad u Ithran bad u Kheran.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Ki khun shynrang u Eser: u Bilhan bad u Saaban, u Jaakan. Ki khun shynrang u Dishan: u Us bad u Aran.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Te kine ki long ki syiem kiba la synshar ha ka ri Edom, mynba ym pat ju synshar da u syiem halor ki khun Israel; u Bela u khun u Beor; bad ka kyrteng ka shnong jong u ka la long “ka Dinhabah”.",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> Te u Bela u la ïap, bad u Jobab u khun u Serah uba na Bosrah u la synshar ha ka jaka jong u.",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> Bad u Jobab u la ïap, bad u Husham uba na ka ri ki Teman u la synshar ha ka jaka jong u.",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> Bad u Husham u la ïap, bad u Hadad u khun u Bedad, uba la pom ïa u Midian ha ka lyngkha u Moab, u la synshar ha ka jaka jong u: te ka kyrteng ka shnong jong u ka la long “ka Abith”.",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> Bad u Hadad u la ïap, bad u Samlah uba na Masrekah u la synshar ha ka jaka jong u.",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> Bad u Samlah u la ïap, bad u Shaul uba na Rehoboth hajan ka Wah u la synshar ha ka jaka jong u.",
			"49": "<sup>49</sup> Bad u Shaul u la ïap, bad u Baal-hanan u khun u Akhbor u la synshar ha ka jaka jong u.",
			"50": "<sup>50</sup> Bad u Baal-hanan u la ïap, bad u Hadad u la synshar ha ka jaka jong u; te ka kyrteng ka shnong jong u ka la long “ka Pai”: bad ka kyrteng ka tnga jong u ka la long “ka Mehetabel”, ka khun ka Matred, ka khun ka Mesahab.",
			"51": "<sup>51</sup> Bad u Hadad u la ïap. Bad ki doloi ka Edom ki la long; u Timna doloi, u Aliah doloi, u Jetheth doloi;",
			"52": "<sup>52</sup> u Oholibamah doloi, u Elah doloi, u Pinon doloi;",
			"53": "<sup>53</sup> u Kenas doloi, u Teman doloi, u Mibsar doloi;",
			"54": "<sup>54</sup> u Magdiel doloi, u Iram doloi. Kine ki long ki doloi ka Edom."
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Kine ki long ki khun shynrang u Israel: u Reuben, u Simeon, u Lebi, bad u Judah, u Issakhar bad u Sabulon;",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> u Dan, u Joseph bad u Benjamin, u Naphtali, u Gad bad u Asher.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ki khun shynrang u Judah: u Er, bad u Onan, bad u Shelah: ïa kine lai ngut la kha ha u na ka Bathshua ka nong Kanaan. Te u Er, u khun nyngkong u Judah, u la long bymman ha khmat U Trai; U ruh U la pynïap ïa u.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad ka Tamar ka pyrsa kurim jong u ka la kha ha u ïa u Peres bad u Serah. Baroh ki khun shynrang u Judah ki la long san ngut.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ki khun shynrang u Peres: u Hesron bad u Hamul.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Serah: u Simri, bad u Ethan, bad u Heman, bad u Kalkol, bad u Dara. Kine baroh ki long san ngut.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Karmi: u Akhar, u nongpynjynjar ïa ki Israel, uba la leh palat ha kata ïa kaba la tim.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Ethan: u Asariah.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ki khun shynrang u Hesron ruh, ïa kiba la kha ha u: u Jerahmil, bad u Ram, bad u Khelubai.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad u Ram u la pynkha ïa u Amminadab; bad u Amminadab u la pynkha ïa u Nahshon, u rangbah ki khun Judah;",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> bad u Nahshon u la pynkha ïa u Salma, bad u Salma u la pynkha ïa u Boas;",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> bad u Boas u la pynkha ïa u Obed, bad u Obed u la pynkha ïa u Jesse;",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> bad u Jesse u la pynkha ïa u khun nyngkong jong u, u Eliab, bad ïa u Abinadab u ba-ar, bad ïa u Shimea u balai;",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> u Nethaniil u basaw, u Raddai u basan;",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> u Osem u bahynriew, u Dabid u bahynñiew;",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> bad ki para kynthei jong ki, ki la long ka Seruïah bad ka Abigail. Bad ki khun shynrang ka Seruïah: u Abishai, bad u Joab, bad u Asahel, lai ngut.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad ka Abigail ka la kha ïa u Amasa: te u kpa u Amasa u la long u Jether u kynja Ishmael.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad u Kaleb u khun u Hesron u la pynkha khun na ka Asubah ka tnga jong u, bad na ka Jerioth: te kine ki la long ki khun shynrang jong ka: u Jesher, bad u Shobab, bad u Ardon.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Te ka Asubah ka la ïap, bad u Kaleb u shim ha u ïa ka Ephrath, kaba la kha ïa u Hur ha u.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad u Hur u la pynkha ïa u Uri, bad u Uri u la pynkha ïa u Besalil.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad hadien kata, u Hesron u la leit ha ka khun u Makhir u kpa u Gilead; ïa kaba u la shim kurim haba u la hynriewphew snem ka rta; te ka la kha ïa u Segub ha u.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Bad u Segub u la pynkha ïa u Jair, uba la don arphew lai tylli ki shnong ha ka ri Gilead.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Bad u Geshur bad u Aram ki la knieh noh ïa ki shnong u Jair na ki, lem bad ka Kenath, bad ki nongrit jong ka, jin hynriewphew ki shnong. Kine baroh ki la long ki khun shynrang u Makhir u kpa u Gilead.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Bad hadien ba la ïap u Hesron ha Kaleb-ephrathah, te ka Abiah ka tnga u Hesron ka la kha ha u, ïa u Ashur u kpa u Tekoa.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Jerahmil u khun nyngkong u Hesron ki la long u Ram u khun nyngkong, bad u Bunah, bad u Oren, bad u Osem, u Ahijah.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Bad u Jerahmil u la don kawei pat ka tnga, kaba kyrteng “ka Atarah”; ka, ka la long ka kmie u Onam.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Ram u khun nyngkong u Jerahmil ki la long u Maas, bad u Jamin, bad u Eker.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Onam ki la long u Shammai, bad u Jada; bad ki khun shynrang u Shammai: u Nadab, bad u Abishur.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Bad ka kyrteng ka tnga u Abishur ka la long “ka Abihail”; te ka la kha ha u, ïa u Ahban, bad u Molid.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Nadab: u Seled, bad u Appaim: hynrei, u Seled u la ïap khlem khun.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Appaim: u Ishi. Bad ki khun shynrang u Ishi: u Sheshan. Bad ki khun shynrang u Sheshan: u Ahlai.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Jada u para u Shammai: u Jether, bad u Jonathan; te u Jether u la ïap khlem khun.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Jonathan: u Peleth, bad u Sasa. Kita ki la long ki khun shynrang u Jerahmil.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Te u Sheshan um shym don ki khun shynrang, tang ki khun kynthei. Bad u Sheshan u la don u shakri, u nong Ijipt, uba kyrteng, “u Jarha”.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Bad u Sheshan u la ai kurim ïa la ka khun ha u Jarha u shakri jong u; te ka la kha ïa u Attai ha u.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Te u Attai u la pynkha ïa u Nathan, bad u Nathan u la pynkha ïa u Sabad;",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> bad u Sabad u la pynkha ïa u Ephlal, bad u Ephlal u la pynkha ïa u Obed;",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> bad u Obed u la pynkha ïa u Jehu, bad u Jehu u la pynkha ïa u Asaraïah;",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> bad u Asaraïah u la pynkha ïa u Heles, bad u Heles u la pynkha ïa u Eleasah;",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> bad u Eleasah u la pynkha ïa u Sismai, bad u Sismai u la pynkha ïa u Shallum;",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> bad u Shallum u la pynkha ïa u Jekamiah, bad u Jekamiah u la pynkha ïa u Elishama.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Te ki khun shynrang u Kaleb u para u Jerahmil ki la long u Mesha u khun nyngkong jong u, uba la long u kpa u Siph; bad ki khun shynrang u Mareshah u kpa u Hebron.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Te ki khun shynrang u Hebron: u Korah, bad u Tappuah, bad u Rekem, bad u Shema.",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> Bad u Shema u la pynkha ïa u Raham, u kpa u Jorkeam; bad u Rekem u la pynkha ïa u Shammai.",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> Bad u khun u Shammai long u Maon; bad u Maon u la long u kpa u Beth-sur.",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> Bad ka Ephah, ka tnga kliar u Kaleb, ka la kha ïa u Haran, bad u Mosa, bad u Gases: bad u Haran u la pynkha ïa u Gases:",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Jahdai; u Regem, bad u Jotham, bad u Geshan, bad u Pelet, bad u Ephah, bad u Shaaph.",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> Ka Maakah, ka tnga kliar u Kaleb, ka la kha ïa u Sheber bad u Tirhanah.",
			"49": "<sup>49</sup> Ka la kha ruh ïa u Shaaph u kpa u Madmannah, u Sheba u kpa u Makhbena, bad u kpa u Gibea; bad ka khun u Kaleb ka la long ka Akhsah.",
			"50": "<sup>50</sup> Kine ki la long ki khun shynrang u Kaleb. U khun u Hur, u khun nyngkong u Ephrathah, u Shobal u kpa u Kiriath-jearim;",
			"51": "<sup>51</sup> u Salma u kpa u Bethlehem, u Hareph u kpa u Beth-gader.",
			"52": "<sup>52</sup> Bad u Shobal u kpa u Kiriath-jearim u la don khun shynrang: u Haroeh, shiteng ki Menuhoth.",
			"53": "<sup>53</sup> Bad ki kur u Kiriath-jearim: ki Ithri, bad ki Puth, bad ki Shumath, bad ki Mishra; na kita ki la mih ki Sorath, bad ki Eshtaol.",
			"54": "<sup>54</sup> Ki khun shynrang u Salma: u Bethlehem, bad ki Netophath, u Atroth-beth-Joab, bad shiteng ki Manahath, ki Sor.",
			"55": "<sup>55</sup> Ki kur nongthoh kiba ju shong ha Jabes: ki Tirath, ki Shimeath, ki Sukath. Kine ki la long ki Ken kiba mih na u Hammath, u kpa ka ïing u Rekhab."
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Kine te ki la long ki khun shynrang u Dabid, ïa kiba la kha ha u ha Hebron: u khun nyngkong, u Amnon, na ka Ahinoam ka nong Jesril; u ba-ar, u Daniel, na ka Abigail ka nong Karmel;",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> u balai, u Absalom u khun ka Maakah ka khun u Talmai u syiem ka Geshur; u basaw, u Adonijah u khun ka Haggith;",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> u basan, u Shephatiah na ka Abital; u bahynriew, u Ithream na ka Eglah ka tnga jong u.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Hynriew ngut la kha ha u ha Hebron; bad u la synshar hangta hynñiew snem hynriew bnai: bad ha Jerusalem u la synshar laiphew lai snem.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad la kha ïa kine ha u ha Jerusalem: u Shimea, bad u Shobab, bad u Nathan, bad u Solomon, saw ngut, na ka Bathshua ka khun u Ammiel:",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> bad u Ibhar, bad u Elishama, bad u Eliphelet;",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> bad u Nogah, bad u Nepheg, bad u Japhia",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> bad u Elishama, bad u Eliada, bad u Eliphelet, khyndai ngut.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Kine baroh ki la long ki khun shynrang u Dabid, nalor ki khun shynrang jong ki tnga kliar; bad ka Tamar ka la long ka para jong ki.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad u khun u Solomon u la long u Rehoboam, u Abijah u khun jong u, u Asa u khun jong u, u Jehoshaphat u khun jong u;",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> u Joram u khun jong u, u Ahasaïah u khun jong u, u Joash u khun jong u:",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> u Amasaïah u khun jong u, u Asaraïah u khun jong u, u Jotham u khun jong u;",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> u Ahas u khun jong u, u Hesekaïah u khun jong u, u Manasseh u khun jong u;",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> u Amon u khun jong u, u Josaïah u khun jong u.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Josaïah; u khun nyngkong u Johanan, u ba-ar u Jehoïakim, u balai u Sedekaïah, u basaw u Shallum.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Jehoïakim: u Jekonaïah u khun jong u, u Sedekaïah u khun jong u.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Jekonaïah, ïa uba la ring mraw; u Shealtiel u khun jong u,",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> bad u Malkhiram, bad u Pedaïah, bad u Shenassar, u Jekamiah, u Hoshama, bad u Nedabiah.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Pedaïah; u Serubbabel, bad u Shimei: bad ki khun shynrang u Serubbabel; u Meshullam, bad u Hananaïah; bad ka Shelomith ka la long ka para jong ki:",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> bad u Hashubah, bad u Ohel, bad u Berekhaïah, bad u Hasadaïah, u Jushab-hesed, san ngut.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Hananaïah: u Pelataïah, bad u Jeshaïah, ki khun shynrang u Rephaïah, ki khun shynrang u Arnan, ki khun shynrang u Obadaïah, ki khun shynrang u Shekanaïah.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Shekanaïah; u Shemaïah: bad ki khun shynrang u Shemaïah: u Hattush, bad u Igal, bad u Bariah, bad u Neariah, bad u Shaphat, hynriew ngut.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Neariah: u Elioenai, bad u Hiskiah, bad u Asrikam, lai ngut.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Elioenai: u Hodabiah, bad u Eliashib, bad u Pelaïah, bad u Akkub, bad u Johanan, bad u Delaïah bad u Anani, hynñiew ngut."
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ki khun shynrang u Judah: u Peres, u Hesron, bad u Karmi, bad u Hur, bad u Shobal.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u Reaïah u khun u Shobal u la pynkha ïa u Jahath; bad u Jahath u la pynkha ïa u Ahumai bad u Lahad. Kine ki long ki kur ki Sorath.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad kine ki la long ki khun shynrang u kpa u Etam: u Jesril, bad u Ishma, bad u Idbash; bad ka kyrteng ka para jong ki ka la long “ka Hasselelponi”;",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> bad u Penuel u kpa u Gedor, bad u Eser u kpa u Hushah. Kine ki long ki khun shynrang u Hur, u khun nyngkong u Ephrathah, u kpa u Bethlehem.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad u Ashur u kpa u Tekoa u la don ar ngut ki tnga: ka Helah bad ka Naarah.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad ka Naarah ka la kha ha u ïa u Ahussam, bad u Hepher, bad u Temeni, bad u Haahashtari. Kine ki la long ki khun shynrang ka Naarah.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang ka Helah ki la long u Sereth, u Ishar, bad u Ethnan.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad u Kos u la pynkha ïa u Anub, bad u Sobebah, bad ïa ki kur u Aharhel u khun u Harum.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te u Jabes u la long uba kham donburom ban ïa ki para jong u: bad ka kmie jong u ka la kyrteng “u Jabes” ïa u, ka da ong, “Namar nga la kha ïa u ha ka sngewsih.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad u Jabes u la kyrpad ha U Blei u Israel, u da ong, “A ban da men kyrkhu ïa nga da shisha, bad ba men pynkylluid ïa ka pud jong nga, bad ba ka kti jong me kan long lem bad nga, bad ba men sumar ïa nga na ka basniew, ba kan ym long ka jingsngewsih ïa nga!” Bad U Blei u la ai ha u, ïa kata kaba u la pan.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad u Khelub u para u Shuhah u la pynkha ïa u Mehir, uba la long u kpa u Eshton.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad u Eshton u la pynkha ïa u Beth-rapha, bad u Paseah, bad u Tehinnah u kpa u Ir-nahash. Kine ki long ki briew ka Rekah.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Kenas: u Othniel, bad u Seraïah; bad ki khun shynrang u Othniel: u Hathath.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad u Meonothai u la pynkha ïa u Ophrah; bad u Seraïah u la pynkha ïa u Joab u kpa ki Geharash; naba ki la long ki nongtrei stad.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Kaleb u khun u Jephunneh: u Iru, u Elah, bad u Naam; bad ki khun shynrang u Elah: u Kenas.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Jehallelel: u Siph, bad u Siphah, u Tiria, bad u Asarel.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Esrah: u Jether, bad u Mered, bad u Epher, bad u Jalon: bad ka la kha ïa ka Miriam, bad u Shammai, bad u Ishbah u kpa u Eshtemoa.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad ka tnga jong u ka kynja Jiw ka la kha ïa u Jered u kpa u Gedor, bad u Heber u kpa u Soko, bad u Jekuthiel u kpa u Sanoah. Bad kine ki long ki khun shynrang ka Bithiah ka khun u Pharaoh, ïa kaba u Mered u la shim.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang ka tnga u Hodiah, ka para u Naham, ki la long u kpa u Keilah u nong Garm, bad u Eshtemoa u nong Maakath.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Shimon: u Amnon, bad u Rinnah, u Benhanan, bad u Tilon. Bad ki khun shynrang u Ishi: u Soheth, bad u Ben-soheth.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ki khun shynrang u Shelah u khun u Judah: u Er u kpa u Lekah, bad u Laadah u kpa u Mareshah, bad ki kur ka ïing jong kita kiba trei ki jaiñ linen bani, na ka ïing u Ashbea;",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> bad u Jokim, bad ki briew ka Koseba, bad u Joash, bad u Saraph, uba la don ka jingsynshar ha Moab, bad u Jashubi-lehem. Te kine ki ktien ki long na mynbarim.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Kine ki la long ki nongthaw khiew, bad kiba shong ha Netaim bad ha Gederah: ki la shong hangta bad u syiem na ka bynta ka kam jong u.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Ki khun shynrang u Simeon: u Nemuel, bad u Jamin, u Jarib, u Serah, u Shaul;",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> u Shallum u khun jong u, u Mibsam u khun jong u, u Mishma u khun jong u.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Mishma: u Hammuel u khun jong u, u Sakkur u khun jong u, u Shimei u khun jong u.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Bad u Shimei u la don khathynriew ngut ki khun shynrang bad hynriew ngut ki khun kynthei; hynrei, ki para jong u kim shym don bun khun, lymne kim shym roi ki kur jong ki baroh kum ki khun u Judah.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Bad ki la shong ha Beer-sheba, bad Moladah, bad Hasar-shual;",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> bad ha Bilhah, bad ha Esem, bad ha Tolad;",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> bad ha Bethuel, bad ha Hormah, bad ha Siklag;",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> bad ha Beth-markaboth, bad ha Hasar-susim, bad ha Beth-biri, bad ha Shaaraim. Kine ki la long ki shnong jong ki haduh ka jingsynshar u Dabid.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Bad ki nongrit jong ki, ki la long ka Etam, ka Ain, ka Rimmon, bad ka Tokhen, bad ka Ashan, san tylli ki shnong:",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> bad baroh ki nongrit jong ki kiba la don baroh sawdong ïa kita ki shnong, haduh ka Baal. Kine ki la long ki jaka shong jong ki, bad ki don la ki jingkha pateng.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Bad u Meshobab, bad u Jamlekh, bad u Joshah u khun u Amasaïah;",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> bad u Joel, bad u Jehu u khun u Joshibiah, u khun u Seraïah, u khun u Asiel;",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> bad u Elioenai, bad u Jaakobah bad u Jeshohaïah, bad u Asaïah, bad u Adiel, bad u Jesimiel, bad u Benaïah;",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> bad u Sisa u khun u Shiphi, u khun u Allon, u khun u Jedaïah, u khun u Shimri, u khun u Shemaïah —",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> kine ïa kiba la ïathuh kyrteng, ki la long ki rangbah ha la ki kur: bad ki ïing ki kpa jong ki, ki la roi shibun.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Bad ki la leit haduh kaba rung sha Gedor, jin haduh ka phang mihngi jong ka them, ban wad ka jaka phlang ïa ki kynhun jong ki.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Bad ki la shem ka jaka phlang kaba sboh bad ka babha, bad ka ri ka la long kaba kylluid, bad kaba jar jar, bad kaba suk; naba kita kiba ju shong hangta mynshuwa, ki la long na ka jong u Ham.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Bad kine ïa kiba la thoh da ka kyrteng, ki la wan ha ki sngi u Hesekaïah u syiem ka Judah, bad ki la pom ïa ki ïingjaiñ jong ki, bad ïa ki Meunim ba la shem hangta, bad ki la pynduh noh khoit ïa ki, haduh kane ka sngi, bad ki la shong duh ha ka jaka jong ki: namar ba la don ka jaka phlang hangta ïa ki kynhun jong ki.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Bad na kine, kata, na ki khun u Simeon, don sanspah ngut ki rangbah kiba la leit sha u lum Seir, ki kaptan jong ki: u Pelatiah, bad u Neariah, bad u Rephaïah, bad u Ussiel, ki khun shynrang u Ishi.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Bad ki la pom ïa kiba dang sah na ki Amalek kiba la lait, bad ki la shong hangta, haduh kane ka sngi."
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Reuben u khun nyngkong jong u Israel, (naba u la long u khun nyngkong; hynrei, namar ba u la pyntngit ïa ka jingthiah u kpa jong u, ïa ka hok ka jinglong hynmen jong u la ai ha ki khun shynrang u Joseph u khun u Israel; bad ïa ka jingkha pateng ym dei ban kheiñ katba kum ka jinglong hynmen.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Naba u Judah u la jop halor ki para jong u, bad na u la wan uta u nongïalam; hynrei, ka jinglong hynmen ka la long ka jong u Joseph:)",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> ki khun shynrang u Reuben u khun nyngkong jong u Israel: u Hanokh, bad u Pallu, u Hesron, bad u Karmi.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ki khun shynrang u Joel: u Shemaïah u khun jong u, u Gog u khun jong u, u Shimei u khun jong u;",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> u Mikah u khun jong u, u Reaïah u khun jong u, u Baal u khun jong u;",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> u Birah u khun jong u, ïa uba u Tilgath-pilneser u syiem ka Assyria u la ring mraw noh; u la long u rangbah jong ki Reuben.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad ki para jong u da ki kur jong ki, haba la kheiñ ïa ka jingkha pateng ki jinghiar pateng jong ki: uba kham rangbah, u Jeiel, bad u Sekhariah:",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> bad u Bela u khun u Asas, u khun u Shema, u khun u Joel, uba la shong ha Aroer, jin haduh Nebo bad Baal-meon.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad shaphang mihngi u la shong haduh kaba rung sha ri khlaw na ka wah Ïuphratis: naba ki masi jong ki, ki la nang roi ha ka ri Gilead.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad ha ki sngi u Saul, ki la ïaleh thma ïa ki Hagar, kiba la kyllon da ka kti jong ki: bad ki la shong ha ki ïingjaiñ jong ki ha ka ri baroh shaphang mihngi ïa ka Gilead.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Gad ki la shong ha marpyrshah jong ki, ha ka ri Bashan haduh Salekah:",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> u Joel uba kham rangbah, bad u Shapham u ba-ar, bad u Janai, bad u Shaphat ha Bashan:",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> bad ki para jong ki na ki ïing ki kpa jong ki: u Mikhael, bad u Meshullam, bad u Sheba, bad u Jorai, bad u Jakan, bad u Sia, bad u Eber, hynñiew ngut.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Kine ki la long ki khun shynrang u Abihail u khun u Huri, u khun u Jaroah, u khun u Gilead, u khun u Mikhael, u khun u Jeshishai, u khun u Jahdo, u khun u Bus;",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> u Ahi u khun u Abdiel, u khun u Guni, u rangbah ki ïing ki kpa jong ki.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te ki la shong ha Gilead, ha Bashan, bad ha ki shnong jong ka, bad ha baroh ki rudnong jong ka Sharon, kat haduh ki pud jong ki.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ïa kine baroh, la ñiew da ki jingkha pateng ha ki sngi u Jotham u syiem ka Judah, bad ha ki sngi u Jeroboam u syiem ki Israel.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ki khun shynrang u Reuben, bad ki Gad, bad shiteng ka jaid u Manasseh, ki rangbah bashlur, ki briew kiba lah ban rah stieh rah wait, bad ban siat da ka ryntieh, bad kiba nang ha ka thma, ki la don sawphew saw hajar hynñiewspah hynriewphew, kiba lah ban leit mih ha ka thma.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad ki la ïaleh thma ïa ki Hagar, ïa u Jetur, bad ïa u Naphish, bad ïa u Nodab.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad la ïarap ïa ki ban ïaleh ïa kita, bad la ai noh ïa ki Hagar ha ka kti jong ki, bad ïa baroh kat kiba la don lem bad ki; naba ki la pyrta ha U Blei ha ka thma, bad U la shahshkor ïa ki; namar ba ki la shaniah ha U.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad ki la knieh noh ïa ki jingri jong ki: na ki ut jong ki, sanphew hajar, bad na ki langbrot jong ki, arspah sanphew hajar, bad na ki kadda jong ki, ar hajar, bad na ki briew, shispah hajar.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Naba shibun ki la kyllon ba la pynïap ïa ki, namar kata ka thma ka la long na U Blei. Bad ki la shong ha ka jaka jong ki haduh kata ka jingring mraw.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Bad ki khun jong kata ka shiteng ka jaid u Manasseh ki la shong ha ka ri: ki la nang roi naduh Bashan haduh Baal-hermon bad Senir bad u lum Hermon.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Bad kine ki la long ki rangbah ka ïing ki kpa jong ki, kata: u Epher, bad u Ishi; bad u Eliel, bad u Asriel, bad u Jeremaïah, bad u Hodabiah, bad u Jahdiel, ki rangbah bashlur, ki rangbah ba-donnam, ki rangbah ki ïing ki kpa jong ki.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Te ki la leh palat ïa U Blei ki kpa jong ki, bad ki la leit klim hadien ki blei jong ki kynja bynriew jong kata ka ri, ïa kiba U Blei u la pynduh noh ha khmat jong ki.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Bad U Blei ki Israel u la pynkhih ïa ka mynsiem u Pul u syiem ka Assyria, bad ïa ka mynsiem u Tilgath-pilneser u syiem ka Assyria, bad u la ïalam noh ïa ki, kata, ïa ki Reuben, bad ïa ki Gad, bad ïa ka shiteng ka jaid u Manasseh, bad u la leit lam noh ïa ki sha Halah, bad Habor, bad Hara, bad sha ka wah Gosan, haduh kane ka sngi."
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ki khun shynrang u Lebi: u Gershon, u Kohath, bad u Merari.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Kohath: u Amram, u Ishar, bad u Hebron, bad u Ussiel.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad ki khun u Amram: u Aaron, bad u Moses, bad ka Miriam. Bad ki khun shynrang u Aaron: u Nadab, bad u Abihu, u Eleasar, bad u Ithamar.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> U Eleasar u la pynkha ïa u Phinehas, u Phinehas u la pynkha ïa u Abishua;",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> bad u Abishua u la pynkha ïa u Bukki, bad u Bukki u la pynkha ïa u Ussi;",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> bad u Ussi u la pynkha ïa u Serahiah, bad u Serahiah u la pynkha ïa u Meraïoth;",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> u Meraïoth u la pynkha ïa u Amariah, bad u Amariah u la pynkha ïa u Ahitub;",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> bad u Ahitub u la pynkha ïa u Sadok, bad u Sadok u la pynkha ïa u Ahimaas;",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> bad u Ahimaas u la pynkha ïa u Asaraïah, bad u Asaraïah u la pynkha ïa u Johanan;",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> bad u Johanan u la pynkha ïa u Asaraïah, (dei une uba la trei ïa ka kam lyngdoh ha kata ka ïing ba u la tei u Solomon ha Jerusalem:)",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> bad u Asaraïah u la pynkha ïa u Amariah, bad u Amariah u la pynkha ïa u Ahitub;",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> bad u Ahitub u la pynkha ïa u Sadok, bad u Sadok u la pynkha ïa u Shallum;",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> bad u Shallum u la pynkha ïa u Hilkiah, bad u Hilkiah u la pynkha ïa u Asaraïah;",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> bad u Asaraïah u la pynkha ïa u Seraïah, bad u Seraïah u la pynkha ïa u Jehosadak;",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> bad u Jehosadak u la leit noh, haba U Trai u pynring mraw ïa ka Judah bad ka Jerusalem da ka kti u Nebukhadnessar.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ki khun shynrang u Lebi: u Gershom, u Kohath, bad u Merari.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad kine ki long ki kyrteng ki khun shynrang u Gershom: u Libni bad u Shimei.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Kohath ki la long u Amram, bad u Ishar, bad u Hebron, bad u Ussiel.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ki khun shynrang u Merari: u Mahli, bad u Mushi. Bad kine ki long ki kur ki Lebi katba kum ki ïing ki kpa jong ki.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na u Gershom: u Libni u khun jong u, u Jahath u khun jong u, u Simmah u khun jong u;",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> u Joah u khun jong u, u Iddo u khun jong u, u Serah u khun jong u, u Jeatherai u khun jong u.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ki khun shynrang u Kohath: u Amminadab u khun jong u, u Korah u khun jong u, u Assir u khun jong u;",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> u Elkanah u khun jong u, bad u Ebiasaph u khun jong u, bad u Assir u khun jong u;",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> u Tahath u khun jong u, u Uriel u khun jong u, u Ussiah u khun jong u, bad u Shaul u khun jong u.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Elkanah: u Amasai, bad u Ahimoth.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Shaphang u Elkanah: ki khun shynrang u Elkanah: u Sophai u khun jong u, bad u Nahath u khun jong u;",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> u Eliab u khun jong u, u Jeroham u khun jong u, u Elkanah u khun jong u.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Samuel: u khun nyngkong u Joel, bad u ba-ar u Abiah.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Ki khun shynrang u Merari: u Mahli, u Libni u khun jong u, u Shimei u khun jong u, u Ussah u khun jong u;",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> u Shimea u khun jong u, u Haggiah u khun jong u, u Asaïah u khun jong u.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Te kine long kita kiba u Dabid u la buh halor ka kam ka jingrwai ha ka ïing U Trai, hadien kaba la ïoh ka jingjahthait ka synduk.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Bad ki la shakri da ka jingrwai ha khmat Ka Tabernakl ka ïingjaiñ ka jingïaseng, tad ynda u Solomon u la tei ka ïing ïa U Trai ha Jerusalem: bad ki la trei ha la ka kam katba kum ka rukom jong ki.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Bad kine ki long kita kiba ïeng, bad ki khun shynrang jong ki. Na ki khun shynrang ki Kohath: u Heman u nongrwai, u khun u Joel, u khun u Samuel;",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> u khun u Elkanah, u khun u Jeroham, u khun u Eliel, u khun u Toah;",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> u khun u Suph, u khun u Elkanah, u khun u Mahath, u khun u Amasai;",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> u khun u Elkanah, u khun u Joel, u khun u Asaraïah, u khun u Sephanaïah;",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> u khun u Tahath, u khun u Assir, u khun u Ebiasaph, u khun u Korah;",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> u khun u Ishar, u khun u Kohath, u khun u Lebi, u khun u Israel.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Bad u Asaph u para jong u, uba ju ïeng ha ka kti kamon jong u, u Asaph u khun u Berekhiah keiñ, u khun u Shimea;",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> u khun u Mikhael, u khun u Baaseïah, u khun u Malkhijah;",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> u khun u Ethni, u khun u Serah, u khun u Adaïah;",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> u khun u Ethan, u khun u Simmah, u khun u Shimei;",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> u khun u Jahath, u khun u Gershom, u khun u Lebi.",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> Bad sha kadiang ki para jong ki, ki khun shynrang u Merari: u Ethan u khun u Kishi, u khun u Abdi, u khun u Mallukh;",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> u khun u Hashabiah, u khun u Amasaïah, u khun u Hilkiah;",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> u khun u Amsi, u khun u Bani, u khun u Shemer;",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> u khun u Mahli, u khun u Mushi, u khun u Merari, u khun u Lebi.",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> Bad ïa ki para jong ki, ki Lebi la thung ïa baroh ka kam Ka Tabernakl ka ïing U Blei.",
			"49": "<sup>49</sup> Hynrei, u Aaron bad ki khun jong u ki la ainguh halor ka duwan ka jingainguh thang, bad halor ka duwan ka jingainguh baiwbih, ïa ka kam baroh ka jong ka jaka kyntang tam, bad ban pynlong ka jingpynïasuk na ka bynta ki Israel, katba kum ïa baroh ba u Moses u shakri U Blei u la lah hukum.",
			"50": "<sup>50</sup> Bad kine ki long ki khun shynrang u Aaron: u Eleasar u khun jong u, u Phinehas u khun jong u, u Abishua u khun jong u;",
			"51": "<sup>51</sup> u Bukki u khun jong u, u Ussi u khun jong u, u Serahiah u khun jong u:",
			"52": "<sup>52</sup> u Meraïoth u khun jong u, u Amariah u khun jong u, u Ahitub u khun jong u;",
			"53": "<sup>53</sup> u Sadok u khun jong u, u Ahimaas u khun jong u.",
			"54": "<sup>54</sup> Te kine ki long ki jaka shong jong ki katba kum ki ilaka jong ki ha ki pud jong ki: ha ki khun shynrang u Aaron, na ki kur ki Kohath, naba ka jong ki ka la long ka bynta banyngkong,",
			"55": "<sup>55</sup> ha ki, ki la ai ka Hebron ha ka ri Judah, bad ki rudnong jong ka baroh sawdong ïa ka;",
			"56": "<sup>56</sup> hynrei, ïa ki lyngkha jong ka shnong, bad ki nongrit jong ka, ki la ai ha u Kaleb u khun u Jephunneh.",
			"57": "<sup>57</sup> Bad ha ki khun shynrang u Aaron ki la ai ki shnong jaka rieh, ïa ka Hebron, ïa ka Libnah ruh bad ki rudnong jong ka, bad ïa ka Jattir, bad ïa ka Eshtemoa bad la ki rudnong;",
			"58": "<sup>58</sup> bad ïa ka Hilen bad la ki rudnong, ïa ka Debir bad la ki rudnong;",
			"59": "<sup>59</sup> bad ïa ka Ashan bad la ki rudnong, bad ïa ka Beth-shemesh bad la ki rudnong;",
			"60": "<sup>60</sup> bad na ka jaid Benjamin, ïa ka Geba bad la ki rudnong, bad ïa ka Alemeth bad la ki rudnong, bad ïa ka Anathoth bad la ki rudnong. Baroh ki shnong jong ki ha ki kur jong ki phar ki la long khatlai tylli ki shnong.",
			"61": "<sup>61</sup> Bad ha kita kiwei na ki khun shynrang u Kohath, la ai da ka jingkhalai, na ka kur jong kata ka jaid, na kata ka shiteng jaid: ka shiteng ka jong u Manasseh, shiphew tylli ki shnong.",
			"62": "<sup>62</sup> Bad ha ki khun shynrang u Gershom, katba kum ki kur jong ki, na ka jaid Issakhar, bad na ka jaid Asher, bad na ka jaid Naphtali, bad na ka jaid Manasseh ha Bashan, khatlai tylli ki shnong.",
			"63": "<sup>63</sup> Ha ki khun shynrang u Merari, la ai da ka jingkhalai, katba kum ki kur jong ki, na ka jaid Reuben, bad na ka jaid Gad, bad na ka jaid Sabulon, khat-ar tylli ki shnong.",
			"64": "<sup>64</sup> Bad ki khun Israel ki la ai ha ki Lebi ïa kita ki shnong lem bad ki rudnong jong ki.",
			"65": "<sup>65</sup> Bad ki la ai da ka jingkhalai na ka jaid ki khun u Judah, bad na ka jaid ki khun u Simeon, bad na ka jaid ki khun u Benjamin, ïa kine ki shnong kiba la ïathuh da ka kyrteng.",
			"66": "<sup>66</sup> Bad katto katne na ki kur ki khun shynrang u Kohath, ki la ïoh ïa ki shnong ki pud jong ki na ka jaid Ephraim.",
			"67": "<sup>67</sup> Bad ki la ai ha ki, ki shnong jaka rieh, ïa ka Shekhem ha ri lum Ephraim bad la ki rudnong; ïa ka Geser ruh bad la ki rudnong;",
			"68": "<sup>68</sup> bad ïa ka Jokmeam bad la ki rudnong, bad ïa ka Beth-horon bad la ki rudnong;",
			"69": "<sup>69</sup> bad ïa ka Aijalon bad la ki rudnong, bad ïa ka Gath-rimmon bad la ki rudnong:",
			"70": "<sup>70</sup> bad na ka shiteng ka jaid u Manasseh, ïa ka Aner bad la ki rudnong, bad ïa ka Bileam bad la ki rudnong; ïa kita kiwei na ka kur ki khun shynrang u Kohath.",
			"71": "<sup>71</sup> Ha ki khun shynrang u Gershom, la ai na ka kur jong ka shiteng ka jaid u Manasseh, ïa ka Golan ha Bashan bad la ki rudnong, bad ïa ka Ashtaroth bad la ki rudnong:",
			"72": "<sup>72</sup> bad na ka jaid Issakhar; ïa ka Kedesh bad la ki rudnong, ïa ka Daberath bad la ki rudnong;",
			"73": "<sup>73</sup> bad ïa ka Ramoth bad la ki rudnong, bad ïa ka Anem bad la ki rudnong;",
			"74": "<sup>74</sup> bad na ka jaid Asher; ïa ka Mashal bad la ki rudnong, bad ïa ka Abdon bad la ki rudnong;",
			"75": "<sup>75</sup> bad ïa ka Hukok bad la ki rudnong, bad ïa ka Rehob bad la ki rudnong:",
			"76": "<sup>76</sup> bad na ka jaid Naphtali; ïa ka Kedesh ha Galilaïa bad la ki rudnong, bad ïa ka Hammon bad la ki rudnong, bad ïa ka Kiriathaim bad la ki rudnong.",
			"77": "<sup>77</sup> Ha kita kiwei na ki Lebi, ïa ki khun shynrang u Merari, la ai na ka jaid Sabulon, ïa ka Rimmon bad la ki rudnong, ïa ka Tabor bad la ki rudnong:",
			"78": "<sup>78</sup> bad sha shiliang ka Jordan hajan Jerikho, shaphang mihngi ka Jordan, la ai ha ki, na ka jaid Reuben, ïa ka Beser ha ri khlaw bad la ki rudnong, bad ïa ka Jahsah bad la ki rudnong,",
			"79": "<sup>79</sup> bad ïa ka Kedemoth bad la ki rudnong, bad ïa ka Mephaath bad la ki rudnong;",
			"80": "<sup>80</sup> bad na ka jaid Gad; ïa ka Ramoth ha Gilead bad la ki rudnong, bad ïa ka Mahanaim bad la ki rudnong,",
			"81": "<sup>81</sup> bad ïa ka Heshbon bad la ki rudnong, bad ïa ka Jaser bad la ki rudnong."
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad na ki khun shynrang u Issakhar: u Tola, bad u Puah, u Jashub, bad u Shimron, saw ngut.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Tola: u Ussi, bad u Rephaïah, bad u Jeriel, bad u Jahmai, bad u Ibsam, bad u Shemuel, ki rangbah ki ïing ki kpa jong ki, kata, na u Tola; ki rangbah bashlur ha la ki pateng bynriew: ka jingkheiñ jong ki ha ki sngi u Dabid ka la long arphew ar hajar bad hynriewspah.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Ussi: u Israhiah; bad ki khun shynrang u Israhiah: u Mikhael, bad u Obadaïah, bad u Joel, u Isshiah, san ngut; baroh kiba rangbah ki briew.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad lem bad ki, ha ki jingkha pateng jong ki, katba kum ki ïing ki kpa jong ki, ki la don ki kynhun ki paidïapom ïa ka thma, laiphew hynriew hajar: namar ki la don shibun ki tnga bad ki khun shynrang.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad ki para jong ki hapdeng ki kur baroh jong u Issakhar, ki rangbah bashlur, ba la ñiew baroh da ka jingkha pateng, ki la long phraphew hynñiew hajar.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ki khun shynrang u Benjamin: u Bela, bad u Bekher, bad u Jediael, lai ngut.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Bela: u Esbon, bad u Ussi, bad u Ussiel, bad u Jerimoth bad u Iri, san ngut; ki rangbah ki ïing ki kpa, ki rangbah bashlur; bad la ñiew ïa ki da ka jingkha pateng, arphew ar hajar bad laiphew saw ngut.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Bekher: u Semirah, bad u Joash, bad u Elieser, bad u Elioenai, bad u Omri, bad u Jeremoth, bad u Abijah, bad u Anathoth, bad u Elemeth. Kine baroh ki la long ki khun u Bekher.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad la ñiew ïa ki da ka jingkha pateng, katba kum ki jinghiar pateng jong ki, ki rangbah ki ïing ki kpa jong ki, ki rangbah bashlur, arphew hajar bad arspah.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Jediael: u Bilhan; bad ki khun shynrang u Bilhan: u Jeush, bad u Benjamin, bad u Ehud, bad u Khenaanah, bad u Sethan, bad u Tarshish, bad u Ahishahar.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Kine baroh ki la long ki khun u Jediael, katba kum ki rangbah ki ïing ki kpa jong ki, ki rangbah bashlur, khathynñiew hajar bad arspah, kiba lah ban leit mih ha u paidïapom ïa ka thma.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> U Shuppim ruh, bad u Huppim, ki khun u Ir, u Hushim, ki khun u Aher.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ki khun shynrang u Naphtali: u Jahsiel, bad u Guni, bad u Jeser, bad u Shallum, ki khun ka Bilhah.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ki khun shynrang u Manasseh: u Asriel, ïa uba ka tnga jong u ka la kha: (ka tnga kliar jong u ka nong Aram ka la kha ïa u Makhir u kpa u Gilead:",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> bad u Makhir u la shim ka tnga na jong u Huppim bad Shuppim, kaba ka kyrteng ka para jong ka, ka la long “ka Maakah”); bad ka kyrteng u ba-ar ka la long “u Selophehad”; bad u Selophehad u la don ki khun kynthei.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad ka Maakah ka tnga u Makhir ka la kha u khun, bad ka la kyrteng “u Peresh” ïa u; bad ka kyrteng u para jong u ka la long “u Sheresh”; bad ki khun shynrang jong u ki la long u Ulam bad u Rakem.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Ulam: u Bedan. Kine ki la long ki khun shynrang u Gilead u khun u Makhir, u khun u Manasseh.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad ka para jong u ka Hammolekheth ka la kha ïa u Ishhod, bad u Abieser, bad u Mahlah.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Shemida ki la long u Ahian, bad u Shekhem, bad u Likhi, bad u Aniam.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Ephraim; u Shuthelah, bad u Bered u khun jong u, bad u Tahath u khun jong u, bad u Eleadah u khun jong u, bad u Tahath u khun jong u,",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> bad u Sabad, u khun jong u, bad u Shuthelah u khun jong u, bad u Eser, bad u Elead, ïa kiba ki nong Gath kiba la kha ha ka ri ki la pynïap, namar ba ki la wan hiar ban knieh noh ïa ki jingri jong ki.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Bad u Ephraim u kpa jong ki u la ïambriew bun sngi, bad ki para jong u ki la wan ban pyntngen ïa u.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Bad u la leit rung sha la ka tnga, te ka la pun, bad ka la kha ïa u khun, bad u la kyrteng “u Beriah” ïa u, namar ba la jia ka basniew ïa ka ïing jong u.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Bad ka khun jong u ka la long “ka Sheerah”, kaba la tei ïa ka Beth-horon kaba sharum bad kaba shaneng, bad ïa ka Ussen-sheerah.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bad u Rephah u la long u khun jong u, bad u Resheph, bad u Telah u khun jong u, bad u Tahan u khun jong u;",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> u Ladan u khun jong u, u Ammihud u khun jong u, u Elishama u khun jong u;",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> u Nun u khun jong u, u Joshua u khun jong u.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Te ki jingïoh kynti bad ki jaka shong jong ki, ki la long ka Bethel bad ki shnong jong ka, bad shaphang mihngi ka Naaran, bad shaphang sepngi ka Geser, bad ki shnong jong ki: ka Shikhem ruh bad ki shnong jong ka, haduh ka Assah bad ki shnong jong ka:",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> bad hajan ki pud ki khun u Manasseh, ka Beth-shean bad ki shnong jong ka, ka Taanakh bad ki shnong jong ka, ka Megiddo bad ki shnong jong ka, ka Dor bad ki shnong jong ka. Ha kine ki la shong ki khun u Joseph u khun u Israel.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Ki khun shynrang u Asher: u Imnah, bad u Ishbah, bad u Ishbi, bad u Beriah, bad ka Serah ka para jong ki.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Beriah: u Heber, bad u Malkhiel, uba la long u kpa u Birsaith.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Bad u Heber u la pynkha ïa u Japhlet, bad u Shomer, bad u Hotham, bad ka Shua ka para jong ki.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Japhlet: u Pasakh, bad u Bimhal, bad u Ashbath. Kine ki long ki khun u Japhlet.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Shemer: u Ahi, bad u Rogah, u Jehubbah, bad u Aram.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Helem u para jong u: u Sophah, bad u Imna, bad u Shelesh, bad u Amal.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Ki khun shynrang u Sophah: u Suah, bad u Harnepher, bad u Shual, bad u Beri, bad u Imrah;",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> U Beser, bad u Hod, bad u Shamma, bad u Shilshah, bad u Ithran, bad u Bira.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Jether: u Jephunneh, bad u Pispa bad u Ara.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Ulla: u Arah, bad u Hanniel, bad u Risia.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Kine baroh ki la long ki khun u Asher, ki rangbah ki ïing ki kpa, ki rangbah kiba la kynsai bad bashlur, kiba ha khlieh ki rangbah. Bad ka jingkheiñ jong ki, ba la ñiew da ka jingkha pateng ïa ka kam ha ka thma ka la long arphew hynriew hajar ki rangbah."
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad u Benjamin u la pynkha ïa u Bela u khun nyngkong jong u, u Ashbel u ba-ar, u Aharah u balai;",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> u Nohah u basaw, bad u Rapha u basan.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad u Bela u la don khun shynrang: u Addar, bad u Gera, bad u Abihud;",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> bad u Abishua, bad u Naaman, bad u Ahoah;",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> bad u Gera, bad u Shephuphan, bad u Huram;",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> bad kine ki long ki khun shynrang u Ehud; kine ki long ki rangbah ki ïing ki kpa jong kiba shong ha Geba, bad ki la ring mraw ïa ki sha Manahath:",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> bad u Naaman, bad u Ahijah, bad u Gera, u la ring mraw ïa ki; bad u la pynkha ïa u Ussa, bad ïa u Ahihud.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad u Shaharaim u la pynkha khun ha ka lyngkha u Moab, hadien kaba u la phah noh ïa ki; ka Hushim bad ka Baara ki la long ki tnga jong u.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad u la pynkha na ka Hodesh ka tnga jong u, ïa u Jobab, bad u Sibia, bad u Mesha, bad u Malkam;",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> bad u Jeus, bad u Shakhia, bad u Mirmah. Kine ki la long ki khun shynrang jong u, ki rangbah ki ïing ki kpa.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad na ka Hushim u la pynkha ïa u Abitub bad u Elpaal.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Elpaal: u Eber, bad u Misham, bad u Shemed, uba la tei ïa ka Ono bad ïa ka Lod, bad ki shnong jong ki:",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> bad u Beriah, bad u Shema, kiba la long ki rangbah ki ïing ki kpa jong kiba shong ha Aijalon, kiba la beh noh ïa kiba shong ha Gath;",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> bad u Ahio, u Shashak, bad u Jeremoth;",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> bad u Sebadiah, bad u Arad, bad u Eder;",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> bad u Mikhael, bad u Ishpah, bad u Joha, ki khun shynrang u Beriah.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad u Sebadiah, bad u Meshullam, bad u Hiski, bad u Heber;",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> bad u Ishmerai, bad u Isliah, bad u Jobab, ki khun u Elpaal;",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> bad u Jakim, bad u Sikhri, bad u Sabdi;",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> bad u Elienai, bad u Sillethai, bad u Eliel;",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> bad u Adaïah, bad u Beraïah, bad u Shimrath, ki khun u Shimei:",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> bad u Ishpan, bad u Eber, bad u Eliel;",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> bad u Abdon, bad u Sikhri, bad u Hanan;",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> bad u Hananiah, bad u Elam, bad u Anthothijah;",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> bad u Iphdeïah, bad u Penuel, ki khun u Shashak;",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> bad u Shamsherai, bad u Shehariah, bad u Athaliah;",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> bad u Jaareshiah, bad u Elijah, bad u Sikhri, ki khun u Jeroham.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Kine ki la long ki rangbah ki ïing ki kpa ha ki jingkha pateng jong ki baroh, ki briew kiba kham rangbah; kine ki la shong ha Jerusalem.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Bad ha Gibeon u la shong u kpa u Gibeon, u Jeiel, uba ka kyrteng ka tnga jong u ka la long “ka Maakah”;",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> bad u khun nyngkong jong u, u Abdon, bad u Sur, bad u Kish, bad u Baal, bad u Nadab,",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> bad u Gedor, bad u Ahio, bad u Sekher.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Bad u Mikloth u la pynkha ïa u Shimeah. Bad ki ruh ki la shong bad la ki para ha Jerusalem, ha marpyrshah ki para jong ki.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Bad u Ner u la pynkha ïa u Kish; bad u Kish u la pynkha ïa u Saul; bad u Saul u la pynkha ïa u Jonathan, bad u Malkhi-shua, bad u Abinadab, bad u Eshbaal.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Bad u khun u Jonathan u la long u Merib-baal; bad u Merib-baal u la pynkha ïa u Mikah.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Mikah: u Pithon, bad u Melekh, bad u Tarea, bad u Ahas.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Bad u Ahas u la pynkha ïa u Jehoaddah; bad u Jehoaddah u la pynkha ïa u Alemeth, u Asmabeth, bad u Simri; bad u Simri u la pynkha ïa u Mosa;",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> bad u Mosa u la pynkha ïa u Binea; u Raphah u la long u khun jong u, u Eleasah u khun jong u, u Asel u khun jong u:",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> bad u Asel u la don hynriew ngut ki khun shynrang kiba ki kyrteng jong ki long kine: u Asrikam, u Bokheru, bad u Ishmael, bad u Sheariah, bad u Obadaïah, bad u Hanan. Kine baroh ki la long ki khun u Asel.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Eshek u para jong u: u Ulam u khun nyngkong jong u, u Jeush u ba-ar, u Eliphelet u balai.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Ulam ki la long ki rangbah ki bashlur, ki nongsiat khnam, bad ki la don bun ki khun shynrang, bad ki ksiew, shispah sanphew. Kine baroh ki la long na ki khun u Benjamin."
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Kumta, ïa ki Israel baroh la kheiñ da ki jinghiar pateng; bad, ha khmih, la thoh ïa ki ha Ka Kitab Ki Syiem Israel: bad ïa ki Judah la ring mraw noh sha Babilon namar ka jingpalat jong ki.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te ki nongshong shnong kiba nyngkong kiba la shong ha la ki bynta bad ha la ki shnong ki la long, ki Israel, ki Lyngdoh, ki Lebi, bad ki Nethin de.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad ha Jerusalem la shong kiba na ki khun u Judah, bad na ki khun u Benjamin, bad na ki khun u Ephraim, bad na ki khun u Manasseh ruh de;",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> u Uthai u khun u Ammihud, u khun u Omri, u khun u Imri, u khun u Bani, na ki khun u Peres u khun u Judah.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad na ki nong Shilon: u Asaïah u khun nyngkong, bad ki khun shynrang jong u.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad na ki khun shynrang u Serah: u Jeuel, bad ki para jong ki, hynriewspah khyndaiphew keiñ.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad na ki khun shynrang u Benjamin: u Sallu u khun u Meshullam, u khun u Hodabiah, u khun u Hassenuah;",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> bad u Ibneïa u khun u Jeroham, bad u Elah u khun u Ussi, u khun u Mikhri, bad u Meshullam u khun u Shephatiah, u khun u Reuel, u khun u Ibnijah;",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> bad ki para jong ki, katba kum ki jinghiar pateng jong ki, ki long khyndaispah sanphew hynriew. Kine baroh ki briew ki la long ki rangbah ki ïing ki kpa katba kum ki ïing ki kpa jong ki keiñ.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad na ki lyngdoh: u Jedaïah, bad u Jehoïarib, u Jakhin;",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> bad u Asaraïah u khun u Hilkiah, u khun u Meshullam, u khun u Sadok, u khun u Meraïoth, u khun u Ahitub, u nongsynshar ka ïing U Blei;",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> bad u Adaïah u khun u Jeroham, u khun u Pashhur, u khun u Malkhijah, bad u Massai u khun u Adiel, u khun u Jahserah, u khun u Meshullam, u khun u Meshillemith, u khun u Immer;",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> bad ki para jong ki, ki rangbah ki ïing ki kpa jong ki, shi hajar hynñiewspah hynriewphew keiñ; ki briew kiba nang shibun ïa ka kam bad ka jingshakri ïa ka ïing U Blei.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad na ki Lebi: u Shemaïah u khun u Hasshub, u khun u Asrikam, u khun u Hashabiah, na ki khun u Merari;",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> bad u Bakbakkar, u Heresh, bad u Galal, bad u Mattaniah u khun u Mika, u khun u Sikhri, u khun u Asaph;",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> bad u Obadaïah u khun u Shemaïah, u khun u Galal, u khun u Jeduthun, bad u Berekhaïah u khun u Asa, u khun u Elkanah, uba shong ha ki nongrit ki Netophath.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad ki nongap khyrdop: u Shallum, bad u Akkub, bad u Talmon, bad u Ahiman, bad ki para jong ki; u Shallum u la long u rangbah;",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> uba haduh kata u la ju ap ha ka khyrdop u syiem shaphang mihngi; ki la long ruh ki nongap khyrdop ïa ki ïingjaiñ ki khun u Lebi.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad u Shallum u khun u Kore, u khun u Ebiasaph, u khun u Korah, bad ki para jong u, kiba na ka ïing u kpa jong u, ki Korah, ki la long halor ka kam ka jingshakri, ki nongsumar ïa ka khyrdop Ka Tabernakl; bad ki kpa jong ki ruh ki la long halor ka ïingjaiñ U Trai, ki nongsumar ka jingkhang;",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> bad u Phinehas u khun u Eleasar u la long u nongsynshar halor jong ki mynshuwa, bad U Trai u la long ryngkat bad u.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> U Sekharaïah u khun jong u Meshelemaïah u la long u nongap jingkhang ha ka ïingjaiñ ka jingïaseng.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Kine baroh kiba la jied ban long ki nongap ha ki khyrdop, ki la long arspah khat-ar ngut. Ïa kine la kheiñ na ki jinghiar pateng ha ki shnong jong ki, ïa kiba u Dabid bad u Samuel u nongïohi ki la thung ha la ka jong ka jong ka kam.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Kumta, kita bad ki khun jong ki, ki la long ki nongkhmih ïa ki khyrdop ka ïing U Trai, ïa ka ïing Ka Tabernakl keiñ, da kaba ap kylliang.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> La don ki nongap ha ki saw ki dong, shaphang mihngi, shaphang sepngi, shaphang shatei, bad shaphang shathie de.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bad ki para jong ki, ha la ki shnong, ki dei ban wan ha la ka aïom aïom ha la hynñiew sngi ban long ryngkat bad ki.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Namar kine ki rangbah nongap khyrdop saw ngut, kiba la long ki Lebi, ki la long ha ka kam ba la buh, bad ki la long halor ki kamra bad halor ki jaka jingkynshew ha ka ïing U Blei.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Bad ki la shong baroh sawdong ka ïing U Blei, namar ka jingsumar jong ka, ka la long ha ki, bad kaba plie ïa ka man la ka step ka la dei ha ki.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Bad la don napdeng jong ki kiba la don ka jingsumar ïa ki pliang ka jingshakri; namar haba ki wallam ïa ki shapoh ki da ñiew ïa ki, bad haba ki sei shabar ki da ñiew ïa ki.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Don na ki ruh ïa kiba la thung halor ki jingbuh jingsat, bad halor ki khiew ki pliang baroh jong ka jaka kyntang, bad halor u 'purew bani, bad ka Waiñ, bad ka umphniang, bad ka jingiwbih, bad ki musla.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Don ruh na ki khun ki lyngdoh kiba la khreh ka jingpynïakhleh ïa ki musla.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Bad u Mattithiah, uwei na ki Lebi, u khun nyngkong u Shallum u jaid Korah, u la don la ka kam ba la buh halor kiei kiei kiba shu shet ha ki pliang.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Don ruh na ki para jong ki, na ki khun u Kohath, kiba la long halor u 'pu pyni, ban khreh ïa u man la ka sngi Sabbaton.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Bad kine ki long ki nongrwai, ki rangbah ki ïing ki kpa na ki Lebi, kiba la shong ha kita ki kamra bad ki lait ruh na kiwei kiwei ki jingshakri: namar ki la trei ha kata ka kam mynsngi bad mynmiet.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Kine ki la long ki rangbah ki ïing ki kpa na ki Lebi, pateng la pateng, ki briew kiba rangbah: kine ki la shong ha Jerusalem.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Bad ha Gibeon u la shong u kpa u Gibeon, u Jeiel keiñ, uba ka kyrteng ka tnga jong u ka la long “ka Maakah”:",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> bad u khun nyngkong jong u, u Abdon, bad u Sur, bad u Kish, bad u Baal, bad u Ner, bad u Nadab,",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> bad u Gedor, bad u Ahio, bad u Sekharaïah, bad u Mikloth.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Bad u Mikloth u la pynkha ïa u Shimeam. Bad ki ruh, ki la shong ryngkat bad la ki para ha Jerusalem, ha marpyrshah ki para jong ki.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Bad u Ner u la pynkha ïa u Kish; bad u Kish u la pynkha ïa u Saul; bad u Saul u la pynkha ïa u Jonathan, bad ïa u Malkhi-shua, bad ïa u Abinadab, bad ïa u Eshbaal de.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Bad u khun u Jonathan u la long u Merib-baal; bad u Merib-baal u la pynkha ïa u Mikah.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Mikah: u Pithon, bad u Melekh, bad u Tarea, bad u Ahas.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Bad u Ahas u la pynkha ïa u Jarah; bad u Jarah u la pynkha ïa u Alemeth, bad ïa u Asmabeth, bad ïa u Simri de; bad u Simri u la pynkha ïa u Mosa:",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> bad u Mosa u la pynkha ïa u Binea; bad u Rephaïah u khun jong u, u Eleasah u khun jong u, u Asel u khun jong u:",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> bad u Asel u la don hynriew ngut ki khun shynrang, ki kyrteng jong ki, ki long kine: u Asrikam, u Bokheru, bad u Ishmael, bad u Sheariah, bad u Obadaïah, bad u Hanan: kine ki la long ki khun u Asel."
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te ki Philistia ki la ïaleh thma ïa ki Israel; bad ki rangbah Israel ki la phet ïap na khmat ki Philistia, bad ki la kyllon ïap ha u lum Gilboa.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad ki Philistia ki la beh eh nadien u Saul bad nadien ki khun jong u; bad ki Philistia ki la pynïap ïa u Jonathan, bad ïa u Abinadab, bad ïa u Malkhi-shua, ki khun u Saul.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad ka thma ka la jur eh pyrshah ïa u Saul, te ki nongsiat khnam ki la lap ïa u; bad u la pisa eh namar kita ki nongsiat khnam.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ynda kumta, u Saul u la ong ha u nongrah atiar jong u, “To sei ïa ka waitlam jong me, bad to dung peib'la ïa nga da ka; ïoh ba kine ki bym-otsher kin ïawan bad kin lehbeiñ ïa nga.” Hynrei, u nongrah atiar jong u, um treh; namar u la sheptieng shibun eh. Namar kata, u Saul u la shim ïa la ka waitlam, bad u la kyllon halor jong ka.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te haba uta u nongrah atiar jong u, u la ïohi ba u Saul u la ïap, u ruh kumjuh u la kyllon halor ka waitlam jong u, bad u la ïap.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Kumta, u Saul u la ïap, bad ki khun jong u ruh lai ngut; bad baroh ka ïing jong u ki la ïap lang.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te haba ki rangbah Israel baroh kiba la don ha kata ka them ki la ïohi ba ki la phet ïap noh, bad ba u Saul bad ki khun jong u ruh ki la ïap, ki la ïa-iehnoh noh ïa ki shnong jong ki, bad ki la phet ïap noh; bad ki Philistia ki la wan bad ki la shong ha ki.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad ha kaba lashai, haba ki Philistia ki la wan ban law jinglaw na kiba la ïap, ki la shem ïa u Saul bad ki khun jong u ba ki la kyllon ha u lum Gilboa.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te ki la law ïa u, bad ki la shim ïa ka khlieh jong u, bad ïa ka jingkieng atiar jong u, bad ki la phah sha ka ri ki Philistia baroh sawdong, ban leit lam ïa ka khubor ha ki blei jong ki, bad ha ki paidbah.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad ki la buh ïa ka jingkieng atiar jong u ha ka ïing ki blei jong ki, bad ki la sieh ïa ka khlieh jong u ha ïing u Dagon.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te haba baroh ki Jabesh-gilead ki la ïohsngew ïa kata baroh kaba ki Philistia ki la leh ïa u Saul,",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> baroh ki riewshlur ki la ïeng bad ki la shim noh ïa ka met u Saul, bad ïa ki met ki khun jong u, bad ki la wallam ïa ki sha Jabesh, bad ki la tep ïa ki shyieng jong ki hapoh u dieng Sning ha Jabesh, bad ki la ïashah jingit hynñiew sngi.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Kumta, u Saul u la ïap namar ka jingpalat jong u kaba u la leh ïa U Trai, na ka bynta kata ka ktien jong U Trai, kaba um shym la sumar; bad namar ba u la ïakylli jingpyrkhat ruh na kawei ka nongkren byrtong, ban ïakylli na ka,",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> bad um shym la kylli na U Trai: namar kata, U la pynïap ïa u, bad U la pynphai noh ïa ka hima sha u Dabid u khun u Jesse."
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ynda kumta, ki Israel baroh ki la ïalang ha u Dabid ha Hebron, ki da ong, “Ha khmih, ngi long ka shyieng bad ka doh jong me.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Wat mynno mynno ruh, haba u Saul u dang long syiem, dei ma me uba la ïalam shabar bad uba la wallam shapoh ha Israel: bad U Trai U Blei jong me u la ong ha me, ‘Men bsa ïa ki briew jong nga ki Israel, bad men long u nongïalam halor ki briew jong nga ki Israel.’ ”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Kumta, ki tymmen basan ki Israel baroh ki la wan sha u syiem ha Hebron; bad u Dabid u la ïateh jutang bad ki ha Hebron ha khmat U Trai; bad ki la pynsleh ïa u Dabid ban long syiem halor ki Israel, katba kum ka ktien U Trai da ka kti u Samuel.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad u Dabid bad ki Israel baroh ki la ïaleit sha Jerusalem (kata ka long “ka Jebus”); bad ki Jebus, ki trai-shnong kata ka ri, ki la don hangta.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad kita kiba shong ha Jebus ki la ong ha u Dabid, “Men ym ïoh wan shane.” Hynrei, pynban, u Dabid u la jop ïa ka kut baskhem ka Seïon; kata ka long “ka nongbah u Dabid.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad u Dabid u la ong, “Jar uba pom nyngkong ïa ki Jebus un long rangbah bad u kaptan.” Bad u Joab u khun ka Seruïah u la leit kiew nyngkong, bad la thung rangbah ïa u.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad u Dabid u la shong ha kata ka kut baskhem; namar kata, ki la khot ïa ka, “ka nongbah u Dabid.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad u la tei ïa kata ka shnong baroh sawdong, naduh Millo baroh sawdong, bad u Joab u la shna ïa kata kawei ka bynta ka jong ka shnong.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad u Dabid u la nang khraw nang khraw; namar U Trai ki paid u la don lem bad u.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te kine ki long kita kiba kongsan na ki riewkhlaiñ kiba u Dabid u la don, kiba la pynkhlaiñ ïa lade bad u ha ka hima jong u, ban pynlong syiem ïa u, ryngkat bad ki Israel baroh, katba kum ka ktien U Trai shaphang ki Israel.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Kane ka long ka jingkheiñ kita ki riewkhlaiñ kiba u Dabid u la don: u Jashobeam, u khun u nong Hakhmon, uba kongsan jong ki laiphew ngut; u la rah ïa la u sum pyrshah ïa ki laispah ngut, bad u la pynïap ïa ki ha kajuh ka por.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad uba bud ha u, u long u Eleasar u khun u Dodo, u nong Ahohi, uba long uwei na ki lai ngut ki riewkhlaiñ.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> U la don lem bad u Dabid ha Pas-dammim, te hangta, ki Philistia ki la ïalum lang ban ïaleh thma, ha kaba la don ka lyngkha kaba dap da u Kew Barli; te ki paidbah ki la phet ïap na ki Philistia.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad ki la ïeng hapdeng kata ka lyngkha, bad ki la ïada ïa ka, bad ki la pynïap ïa ki Philistia; bad U Trai u la pyllait im ïa ki da ka jingjop ka bakhraw.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad lai ngut na ki laiphew ngut ki rangbah ki la leit hiar sha u Dabid ha u mawsiang ha ka krem Adullam; bad u paidïapom ki Philistia u la sher dara ha ka them Rephaim.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad u Dabid ha kata ka por u don hapoh kata ka kut, bad ka karod ki Philistia ka la don ha Bethlehem ha kata ka por.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te u Dabid u la sngew-sliang, bad u la ong, “A ban da don u ban ai um ïa nga ba ngan dih na ka pukri Bethlehem, kaba hajan kata ka khyrdop!”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad kine ki lai ngut ki la tur lyngba u paidïapom ki Philistia, bad ki la tong um na ka pukri Bethlehem, kaba hajan ka khyrdop, ki la shim ïa ka, bad ki la wallam sha u Dabid: hynrei, u Dabid um treh ban dih ïa ka, hynrei, u la theh noh ïa ka ha U Trai,",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> bad u la ong, “U Blei jong nga u khang ïa nga, ba ngan leh kum ïa kane: hato ngan dih ïa ka snam kine ki rangbah kiba la kheiñduh ïa la ka jingim? namar da kaba ki kheiñduh ïa la ka jingim, ki la wallam ïa ka.” Namar kata, um treh ban dih ïa ka. Ïa kine kiei kiei ki la leh kita ki lai ngut ki riewkhlaiñ.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad u Abishai, u para u Joab, u la long uba kongsan na ki lai ngut: namar u la rah ïa la u sum pyrshah ïa ki laispah ngut bad u la pynïap ïa ki, kumta u la donnam hapdeng ki lai ngut.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na ki lai ngut, u la long uba kham donburom ban ïa ki ar ngut, bad la thung ïa u, u kaptan jong ki: la kumta ruh, um shym kot kat ki lai ngut kiba nyngkong.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> U Benaïah u khun u Jehoïada, u khun jong u rangbah bashlur na ka Kabsil, uba la leh ki kam bakhraw, u la pynïap ïa ki ar ngut ki khun shynrang u Ariel uba na Moab: u la leit hiar ruh bad u la pynïap ïa u sing hapdeng ka thliew ha ka por hap ïor.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Bad u la pynïap ïa u nong Ijipt, u briew uba jrong ka rynïeng, ka jingjrong san pruh; bad la don u sum ha ka kti uta u nong Ijipt uba kum u khung jong u nongthain jaiñ; te u la leit sha u bad u diengduh, bad u la knieh kynsan ïa u sum na ka kti une u nong Ijipt, bad u la pynïap ïa u da u sum jong u hi.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Ïa kine kiei kiei u la leh u Benaïah u khun u Jehoïada, bad u la donnam hapdeng kita ki lai ngut ki rangbah badonbor.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Ha khmih, u long uba kham donburom ban ïa ki laiphew ngut, hynrei, um shym kot kat ki lai ngut kiba nyngkong; bad u Dabid u la buh ïa u halor ki nongap phira jong u.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Ki riewdonbor ki paidïapom ruh; u Asahel u para u Joab, u Elhanan u khun u Dodo uba na Bethlehem;",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> u Shammoth u nong Haror, u Heles u nong Pelon;",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> u Ira u khun u Ikkesh u nong Teko, u Abieser u nong Anathoth;",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> u Sibbekai u nong Hushath, u Ilai u nong Ahoh;",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> u Maharai u nong Netophath, u Heled u khun u Baanah u nong Netophath;",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> u Ithai u khun u Ribai uba na Gibeah na ki khun u Benjamin, u Benaïah u nong Pirathon;",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> u Hurai na ki wah duid ka Gaash, u Abiel u nong Arbath;",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> u Asmabeth u nong Baharum, u Eliahba u nong Shaalbon;",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> ki khun u Hashem u nong Gison, u Jonathan u khun u Shage u nong Harar;",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> u Ahiam u khun u Sakar u nong Harar, u Eliphal u khun u Ur;",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> u Hepher u nong Mekherath, u Ahijah u nong Pelon;",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> u Hesro u nong Karmel, u Naarai u khun u Esbai;",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> u Joel u para u Nathan, u Mibhar u khun u Hagri;",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> u Selek u nong Ammon, u Naharai u nong Beeroth, u nongrah atiar u Joab u khun ka Seruïah;",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> u Ira u nong Ithri, u Gareb u nong Ithri;",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> u Uriah u nong Hit, u Sabad u khun u Ahlai;",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> u Adina u khun u Shisa jaid Reuben, uba rangbah na ki Reuben, bad laiphew ngut lem bad u;",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> u Hanan u khun u Maakah, bad u Joshaphat u nong Mithni;",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> u Ussia u nong Ashterath, u Shama bad u Jeiel ki khun u Hotham u nong Aroer;",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> u Jediael u khun u Shimri, bad u Joha u para jong u, u nong Tis;",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> u Eliel u nong Mahab, bad u Jeribai, bad u Joshabiah, ki khun u Elnaam, bad u Ithmah u nong Moab;",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> u Eliel, bad u Obed, bad u Jaasiel u nong Mesoba."
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te kine ki long kita kiba la wan sha u Dabid ha Siklag, haba u dang rieh khop ïa lade namar u Saul u khun u Kish; bad ki long hapdeng ki briew badonbor, ki nongïarap jong u ha ka thma.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ki la long kiba kieng ryntieh, bad kiba nang ban kawang maw bad ban siat khnam na ka ryntieh bad kadiang bad kamon; kine ki long na ki para u Saul na ki Benjamin.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Uba rangbah u long u Ahieser, hadien sa u Joash, ki khun u Shemaah u nong Gibeah; bad u Jesiel, bad u Pelet, ki khun u Asmabeth; bad u Berakah, bad u Jehu u nong Anathoth;",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> bad u Ishmaïah u nong Gibeon, u briew u badonbor hapdeng ki laiphew ngut, bad u la long halor kita ki laiphew ngut; bad u Jeremaïah, bad u Jahasiel, bad u Johanan, bad u Josabad u nong Gederath;",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> u Elusai, bad u Jerimoth, bad u Bealiah, bad u Shemariah, bad u Shephatiah u nong Haruph;",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> u Elkanah, bad u Isshiah, bad u Asarel, bad u Joeser, bad u Jashobeam, ki jaid Korah;",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> bad u Joelah, bad u Sebadiah, ki khun u Jeroham uba na Gedor.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad na ki Gad ki la don kiba la pynkhlad ïa lade sha u Dabid ha ka kut ha ri khlaw, ki riewkhlaiñ ki bashlur, ki rangbah ba la hikai ïa ka thma, kiba nang ban bat stieh bat sum; kiba ki khmat jong ki, ki long kum ki jong ki sing, bad kiba stet kum ki skei halor ki lum;",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> u Eser uba kham rangbah, u ba-ar u Obadaïah, u balai u Eliab;",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> u basaw u Mishmannath, u basan u Jeremaïah;",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> u bahynriew u Attai, u bahynñiew u Eliel;",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> u baphra u Johanan, u bakhyndai u Elsabad;",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> u bashiphew u Jeremaïah, u bakhatwei u Makbannai.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Kine na ki khun shynrang u Gad ki la long ki kaptan ki paidïapom: uta u bapoh tam u biang hi ïa shispah ngut, bad uba rangbah tam u biang hi ïa shi hajar ngut.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Kine ki long kita kiba la ryngkang ïa ka Jordan ha u bnai u banyngkong, haba ka la shlei ïa ki rud jong ka baroh; bad ki la pynher noh ïa kito kiba ha ki them, shaphang mihngi, bad shaphang sepngi.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad la don na ki khun Benjamin bad Judah kiba la wan sha ka kut ha u Dabid.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad u Dabid u la leit tan ïa ki, bad u la ïathuh u ong ruh ha ki, “Lada phi wan sha nga da kaba suk ban ïarap ïa nga, ka dohnud jong nga kan ïasoh ha phi: hynrei, lada phi wan ban die noh ïa nga ha ki nongïaleh pyrshah jong nga, haba ym don jingsniew ha ki kti jong nga, to U Blei ki kpa jong ngi un khmih ïa kata, bad un sneng ïa ka.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ynda kumta, U Mynsiem u la wan ha u Amasai, u rangbah ki laiphew ngut, bad u la ong, “Ngi ki jong me, ko Dabid, bad ha ka liang jong me, ko me u khun u Jesse: to ka jingsuk, ka jingsuk kan long ha me, bad ka jingsuk ha ki nongïarap jong me; naba U Blei jong me u ïarap ïa me.” Ynda kumta, u Dabid u la pdiang ïa ki, bad u la pynlong ïa ki, ki kaptan ka kynhun.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Don ruh na ki Manasseh kiba la kylla sha u Dabid, haba u la wan lem bad ki Philistia ban ïaleh ïa u Saul ha ka thma, hynrei, kim shym ïarap ïa ki: namar ki doloi ki Philistia haba ki la ïapyrkhat ki la phah noh ïa u, ki da ong, “Un kylla noh sha u Saul u kynrad jong u, hangta ngi la pha ïa la ki khlieh.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Katba u dang leit sha Siklag, ki ïakylla sha u na ka jaid Manasseh, u Adnah, bad u Josabad, bad u Jediael, bad u Mikhael, bad u Josabad, bad u Elihu, bad u Sillethai, ki rangbah shihajar kiba na ka jaid Manasseh.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad ki la ïarap ïa u Dabid ban ïaleh ïa ka kynhun nonglute: namar ki la long baroh ki riewkhlaiñ ki bashlur, bad ki la long ki kaptan ha u paidïapom.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Namar man la ka sngi ki la don kiba la wan ha u Dabid ban ïarap ïa u, haduh ban da long u paidbah byllien, kum u paidbah U Blei keiñ.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Bad kine ki long ki jingkheiñ ki rangbah jong ki kiba la kieng atiar ïa ka thma, kiba la wan sha u Dabid ha Hebron, ban pynphai noh ïa ka hima u Saul sha u, katba kum ka ktien U Trai.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Ki khun u Judah kiba rah stieh rah sum ki long hynriew hajar phraspah, kiba la kieng atiar ïa ka thma.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na ki khun u Simeon, ki riewkhlaiñ ki bashlur ïa ka thma, hynñiew hajar bad shispah.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Na ki khun u Lebi, saw hajar hynriewspah.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Bad u Jehoïada u long u nongïalam ka ïing u Aaron, bad lai hajar hynñiewspah kiba bad u;",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> bad u Sadok, u samla u bakhlaiñ uba shlur, bad arphew ar ngut ki kaptan na ka ïing u kpa jong u.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Bad na ki khun u Benjamin, ki para u Saul, lai hajar; naba baroh shi katta kiba kham bun na ki, ki dang kohnguh ïa ka ïing u Saul.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Bad na ki khun u Ephraim ki riewkhlaiñ ki bashlur, ki briew kiba donnam ha ki ïing ki kpa jong ki, arphew hajar phraspah.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Bad na ka shiteng ka jaid u Manasseh, khatphra hajar, kiba la ïathuh kyrteng ban wan pynlong syiem ïa u Dabid.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Bad na ki khun u Issakhar, ki briew kiba don ka jingshemphang ha ki aïom, ban sngewthuh ïa kaei ba ki Israel ki dei ban leh; ki rangbah jong ki, ki long arspah; bad ki para jong ki baroh ki long ha ka hukum jong ki.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Na ka jaid Sabulon, ki kynja ba lah ban leit mih ha u paidïapom, kiba nang ban pynbeit ryntih ïa ka thma, lem bad ki kynja tiar ïapom baroh, sanphew hajar; bad kiba lah ban pynbeit ryntih ïa ka thma, bad ki bym arsap ka dohnud.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Bad na ka jaid Naphtali, shi hajar ki kaptan, bad la don lem bad ki bad stieh bad sum, laiphew hynñiew hajar.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Bad na ka jaid Dan kiba nang ban pynbeit ryntih ïa ka thma, arphew phra hajar hynriewspah.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Bad na ka jaid Asher, ki kynja ba lah ban leit mih ha u paidïapom, kiba nang ban pynbeit ryntih ïa ka thma, sawphew hajar.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Bad sha shiliang ka Jordan, na ka jaid Reuben, bad na ka jaid Gad, bad na ka shiteng ka jaid u Manasseh, kiba don ki kynja tiar ïapom baroh ïa ka thma, shispah arphew hajar.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Kine baroh, kiba long ki riewthma, kiba nang ban buh pynbeit ryntih ïa ka thma, ki la wan da ka dohnud bahok sha Hebron, ban pynlong syiem ïa u Dabid halor ki Israel baroh: bad kita kiwei baroh na ki Israel ki la long da kawei ka dohnud ban pynlong syiem ïa u Dabid.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Bad ki la don hangta bad u Dabid lai sngi, ki da bam ki da dih: namar ki para jong ki, ki la pynkhreh na ka bynta jong ki.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Nalor kata, kito kiba hajan ïa ki, wat haduh Issakhar bad Sabulon bad Naphtali, ki la wallam jingbam halor ki kadda, bad halor ki ut, bad halor ki khashor, bad halor ki masi dab, ki kynja jingbam kiba da u 'purew, ki 'pu soh Dumbur, bad ki rynjup soh Khajur, bad ka Waiñ, bad ka umphniang, bad ki masi dab, bad ki langbrot kyrhai: namar la don ka jingkmen ha Israel."
		},
		"13": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad u Dabid u la ïasylla lem bad ki rangbah shihajar bad ki rangbah shispah, bad ki nongïalam baroh keiñ.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u Dabid u la ong ïa ka jingïaseng lang ki Israel baroh, “Lada phi ibit, bad lada ka long na U Trai U Blei jong ngi, to ngin phah kylleng kylleng sha ki para jong ngi ïa kiba la pynsah ha ka ri Israel baroh, kiba ryngkat bad ki don ki lyngdoh bad ki Lebi ha ki shnong jong ki, kiba don rudnong, ba kin ïawan lang sha ngi:",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> bad to ngin ïawallam pat ïa ka synduk U Blei jong ngi sha ngi hi: namar ngim shym la wad sha ka ha ki sngi u Saul.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad ka jingïaseng lang baroh ka la ong ba kin leh kumta: namar kata ka la long kaba dei ha khmat uta u paidlang baroh.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Kumta, u Dabid u la pynïaseng lang ïa ki Israel baroh, naduh Shihor ka wah Ijipt haduh kaba rung sha Hamath, ïa ka ban wallam ïa ka synduk U Blei na Kiriath-jearim.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad u Dabid u la leit kiew, bad ki Israel baroh, sha Baalah, kata long, sha Kiriath-jearim, kaba dei ïa ka Judah, ban wallam noh nangta ïa ka synduk U Blei, U Trai uba shong halor ki Kherub, ïa kaba la khot da kata ka Kyrteng.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad ki la pynkit ïa ka synduk U Blei halor ka kali thymmai, bad ki la wallam noh ïa ka, na ka ïing u Abinadab: bad u Ussa bad u Ahio ki la ïañiah ïa ka kali.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad u Dabid bad ki Israel baroh ki la tem jingtem ha khmat U Blei da ka bor jong ki baroh: da ki jingrwai, bad da ki duitara, bad da ki nebel, bad da ki kanjari, bad da ki ksing padiah, bad da ki ronsing.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te haba ki la poi ha ka kyntem u Khidon, u Ussa u la sei la ka kti ban bat ïa kata ka synduk, namar ki masi ki la jynthut.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te ka jingbitar U Trai ka la meh pyrshah ïa u Ussa, bad u la shoh ïa u, namar ba u ktah ïa kata ka synduk: bad u la ïap hangta ha khmat U Blei.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad u Dabid u la sngewsih, namar ba U Trai u la kyntur ïa u Ussa: bad u la khot ïa kata ka jaka “ka Peres-ussa,” haduh kane ka sngi.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad u Dabid u la sngewsheptieng ïa U Blei ha kata ka sngi, u da ong, “Kumno ngan leit lam ïa ka synduk U Blei sha la ïing sha nga?”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Kumta, u Dabid um shym pynkynriah ïa ka synduk sha u sha ka shnong u Dabid, hynrei, u la pynkit ïa ka sharud sha ka ïing u Obed-edom u nong Gitt.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad ka synduk U Blei ka la sah bad ki ba-ha-ïing u Obed-edom ha ka ïing jong u, lai bnai: bad U Trai u la kyrkhu ïa ka ïing u Obed-edom, bad ïa baroh katba u don."
		},
		"14": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad u Hiram u syiem ka Tyros u la phah ïa ki nonglam-ktien sha u Dabid, bad ïa ki dieng Kedar, bad ïa ki nongtrei kynroh, bad ïa ki misteri, ban thaw ïing ïa u.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te u Dabid u la tip ba U Trai u la pynskhem ïa u ban long syiem halor ki Israel, namar ïa ka hima jong u la kyntiew hajrong, na ka bynta ki briew jong u ki Israel.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad u Dabid u la shim shuh shuh ki tnga ha Jerusalem: bad u Dabid u la pynkha kham bun shuh ki khun shynrang bad ki kynthei.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad kine ki long ki kyrteng kita ki khun kiba u la ïoh ha Jerusalem: u Shammua, bad u Shobab, u Nathan, bad u Solomon,",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> bad u Ibhar, bad u Elishua, bad u Elphelet,",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> bad u Nogah, bad u Nepheg, bad u Japhia,",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> bad u Elishama, bad u Biliada, bad u Eliphelet.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te haba ki Philistia ki la ïohsngew ba la pynsleh syiem ïa u Dabid halor ki Israel baroh, ki Philistia baroh ki la ïaleit kiew ban wad ïa u Dabid: bad u Dabid u la ïohsngew ïa kata, bad u la leit mih ban ïaleh ïa ki.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te ki Philistia ki la lah wan bad ki la hiar lute ha ka them Rephaim.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad u Dabid u la kylli na U Blei, u da ong, “Ngan leit ïaleh ïa ki Philistia? Te men ai noh ïa ki ha ka kti jong nga?” Bad U Trai u la ong ïa u, “Khie leit; naba ngan ai noh ïa ki ha ka kti jong me.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Kumta, ki la ïawan sha Baal-perasim, bad u Dabid u la shoh jop ïa ki hangta; bad u Dabid u la ong, “U Blei u la pynsaphred ïa ki nongshun jong nga da ka kti jong nga, kumba pynsaphred ïa ki um.” Namar kata, ki la khot kyrteng ïa kata ka jaka “Baal-perasim.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad ki la iehnoh noh ïa ki blei jong ki hangta; bad u Dabid u la ai ka hukum, bad la thang ïa ki da ka ding.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Hynrei, ki Philistia ki la wan hiar lute pat ha kata ka them.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad u Dabid u la kylli pat na U Blei; bad U Blei u la ong ïa u, “Men ym leit beh ïa ki; to phai noh na ki, bad to kyntur sha ki, ha marpyrshah ki dieng Bekaim.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te haba men ïohsngew ïa ka jingsawa kum ka jingïaid ha kliar ki dieng Bekaim, hangta te men leit mih ban ïaleh: namar U Blei u la leit ha shuwa jong me ban shoh ïa u paidïapom ki Philistia.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad u Dabid u la leh kumba U Blei u la hukum ïa u; bad ki la shoh jop ïa u paidïapom ki Philistia naduh Gibeon haduh Geser.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad ka nam u Dabid ka la phriang ha ki ri baroh; bad U Trai u la wallam ka jingsheptieng ïa u ha ki jaid bynriew baroh."
		},
		"15": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad u Dabid u la thaw ki ïing ïa lade ha ka shnong u Dabid; bad u la khreh ka jaka ïa ka synduk U Blei, bad u la pynïeng ka ïingjaiñ na ka bynta jong ka.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te u Dabid u la ong, “Ym bit ïano ïano ban leit rah ïa ka synduk U Blei, hynrei, tang ki Lebi hi: namar U Trai u la jied ïa ki, ban bah ïa ka synduk U Blei, bad ban shakri ïa u junom.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad u Dabid u la lum lang ïa ki Israel baroh ha Jerusalem, ban wallam noh ïa ka synduk U Trai sha ka jaka jong ka, kaba u la pynkhreh ïa ka.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad u Dabid u la lum lang ïa ki khun shynrang u Aaron, bad ïa ki Lebi:",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> na ki khun u Kohath: u Uriel u rangbah, bad ki para jong u, shispah arphew;",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> na ki khun u Merari: u Asaïah u rangbah, bad ki para jong u, arspah arphew;",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> na ki khun u Gershom: u Joel u rangbah, bad ki para jong u, shispah laiphew;",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> na ki khun u Elisaphan: u Shemaïah u rangbah, bad ki para jong u, arspah;",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> na ki khun u Hebron: u Eliel u rangbah, bad ki para jong u, phraphew;",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> na ki khun u Ussiel: u Amminadab u rangbah, bad ki para jong u, shispah khat-ar.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad u Dabid u la phah khot ïa u Sadok bad ïa u Abiathar ki lyngdoh, bad ïa ki Lebi, ïa u Uriel, u Asaïah, bad u Joel, u Shemaïah, bad u Eliel, bad u Amminadab,",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> bad u la ong ïa ki, “Phi long ki rangbah ki ïing ki kpa jong ki Lebi; to pynkyntang ïa lade, ma phi bad ki para jong phi, ba phin wallam artet ïa ka synduk U Trai, U Blei ki Israel, sha ka jaka ba nga la pynkhreh ïa ka.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Namar haba phim shym bah ïa ka ha kaba nyngkong, U Trai U Blei jong ngi u la pynmong ïa ngi, namar ba ngim shym la wad ïa u katba kum ka hukum.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Kumta, ki lyngdoh bad ki Lebi ki la pynkyntang ïa lade ban wallam artet ïa ka synduk U Trai, U Blei ki Israel.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad ki khun ki Lebi ki la ïabah ïa ka synduk U Blei halor ki tyrpeng jong ki lem bad ki dieng jingbah ha ka, kumba u Moses u la hukum katba kum ka ktien U Trai.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad u Dabid u la kren ïa ki rangbah jong ki Lebi ba kin thung ïa ki para jong ki, ki nongrwai, lem bad ki tiar jingtem, ki nebel bad ki duitara bad ki ksing padiah, ban pynsawa jam bad ban pynjam la ka ktien da ka jingkmen.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Kumta, ki Lebi ki la thung ïa u Heman u khun u Joel; bad na ki para jong u, ïa u Asaph u khun jong u Berekaïah; bad na ki khun u Merari ki para jong ki, ïa u Ethan u khun u Kushaïah;",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> bad lem bad ki, ki para jong ki, kiba bud ha ki, u Sekharaïah, u Ben, bad u Jaasiel, bad u Shemiramoth, bad u Jehiel, bad u Unni, u Eliab, bad u Benaïah, bad u Maaseïah, bad u Mattithiah, bad u Eliphelehu, bad u Mikneïah, bad u Obed-edom, bad u Jeiel, ki nongsumar jingkhang.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Kumta, la thung ïa ki nongrwai, ïa u Heman, u Asaph, bad u Ethan, lem bad ki ksing padiah rnong ban pynsawa jam;",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> bad u Sekharaïah, bad u Asiel, bad u Shemiramoth, bad u Jehiel, bad u Unni, bad u Eliab, bad u Maaseïah, bad u Benaïah, da ki nebel ba la buh ïa ka Alamoth;",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> bad u Mattithiah, bad u Eliphelehu, bad u Mikneïah, bad u Obed-edom, bad u Jeiel, bad u Asasiah, da ki duitara ba la buh ïa ka Sheminith, ban ïalam.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Bad u Khenaniah, u rangbah ki Lebi, u la long halor ka jingrwai; u hikai shaphang ka jingrwai, namar u la long uba nang.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Bad u Berekhaïah bad u Elkanah ki la long ki nongap jingkhang ïa kata ka synduk.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Bad u Shebaniah, bad u Joshaphat, bad u Nethanil, bad u Amasai, bad u Sekharaïah, bad u Benaïah, bad u Elieser, ki lyngdoh, ki la put da ki ronsing ha shuwa ka synduk U Blei: bad u Obed-edom bad u Jehiah ki la long ki nongap jingkhang ïa ka synduk ka jutang.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Kumta, u Dabid, bad ki tymmen basan ki Israel, bad ki rangbah shihajar, ki la leit ban wallam artet ïa ka synduk ka jutang U Trai na ka ïing u Obed-edom da ka jingkmen:",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> te haba U Blei u la ïarap ïa ki Lebi kiba bah ïa ka synduk ka jutang U Trai, ki la kñia hynñiew tylli ki masi dab bad hynñiew tylli ki 'lang sohmoh.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Bad u Dabid u la kup da ka jaiñkup linen bani, bad baroh ki Lebi kiba ïabah ïa ka synduk ka jutang, bad ki nongrwai bad u Khenaniah u nonghikai jingrwai lem bad ki nongrwai: bad u Dabid u la phong ka ephod linen.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Kumne ki Israel baroh ki la wallam artet ïa ka synduk ka jutang U Trai da ka jingrisa, bad da ka jingsawa ka jingput, bad ki ronsing, bad da ki 'sing padiah, ki da pynsawa jam da ki nebel bad ki duitara.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Te haba ka synduk ka jutang U Trai ka la wan sha ka shnong u Dabid, ka Mikhal ka khun u Saul ka la khmih na ka jingkhang ïit, bad ka la ïohi ïa u syiem Dabid ba u da shad bad ba u tem; bad ka la ibeiñ ïa u ha ka dohnud jong ka."
		},
		"16": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te ki la wallam hapoh ïa ka synduk U Blei, bad ki la buh ïa ka hapdeng ka ïingjaiñ ïa kaba u Dabid u la pynïeng na ka bynta jong ka: bad ki la ainguh ïa ki jingainguh thang bad ki jingainguh pynïasuk, ha khmat U Blei.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te haba u Dabid u la pyndep kaba ainguh ïa ka jingainguh thang bad ki jingainguh pynïasuk, u la kyrkhu ïa u paidbah ha ka kyrteng U Trai.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad u la ai ha uwei pa kawei na ki Israel, shynrang bad kynthei, ha uwei pa kawei uwei u kpu, bad shi bynta ka doh, bad uwei u 'pu soh Khajur.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad u la thung ïa kiba na ki Lebi ban shakri ha khmat ka synduk ka jutang U Trai, bad ban pyndonburom bad ban ainguh bad ïaroh ïa U Trai, U Blei ki Israel.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> U Asaph u rangbah, bad uba bud ha u, u Sekharaïah, u Jeiel, bad u Shemiramoth, bad u Jehiel, bad u Mattithiah, bad u Eliab, bad u Benaïah, bad u Obed-edom, bad u Jeiel, lem bad ki nebel bad ki duitara; bad u Asaph lem bad ki 'sing padiah, u da pynsawa jam;",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> bad u Benaïah bad u Jahasiel ki lyngdoh lem bad ki turoi borabor, ha khmat ka synduk ka jutang U Blei.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te ha kata ka sngi, u Dabid, ka banyngkong eh u la pynlong ban ainguh ha U Trai, da ka kti u Asaph bad ki para jong u.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> A to ainguh ha U Trai, khot kyrpad ïa ka kyrteng jong u; to pynbna ïa ki jingleh jong u hapdeng ki kynja bynriew.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> To rwai ha u, rwai ïa ki jingïaroh ïa u; to ïakren shaphang ki kam ki baphylla jong u baroh.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> To leh thaw burom ha ka kyrteng bakhuid jong u: to ai ba kan kmen ka dohnud jong kita kiba wad ïa U Trai.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> To wad phi ïa U Trai bad ïa ka bor jong u; wad ïa ka khmat jong u ha la ka sngi.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> To kynmaw ïa ki kam ki baphylla jong u ïa kiba u la leh; ïa ki jingphylla jong u, bad ïa ki jingbishar ka shyntur jong u;",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> ko phi u symbai u Israel u shakri jong u, phi ki khun u Jakob, kiba la jied jong u.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> U long ma u, U Trai uba U Blei jong ngi: ki jingbishar jong u ki ha ka pyrthei baroh.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> To kynmaw ïa ka jutang jong u ha la ka rta, ïa kata ka ktien kaba u la hukum ïa ki hajar ki pateng bynriew;",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> kata ka jutang ïa kaba u la teh bad u Abraham, bad ka jingsmai jong u ha u Isaak;",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> bad u la pynskhem ïa kata ha u Jakob ba kan long ka aiñ, ha u Israel ban long ka jutang bajunom.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> U ong, “Ha me ngan ai ïa ka ri Kanaan, ka bynta ka ri kynti jong phi:”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Mynba phi dang khyndiat briew ha ka jingkheiñ; ho-oid, tang khyndiat eh keiñ, bad ki sohshnong ha ka;",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> bad ba ki ïaleit kylleng na kawei ka jaid bynriew sha kawei ka jaid bynriew, bad na kawei ka hima sha kawei pat ka kynja bynriew.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Um shym la shah ïa uno uno ban leh sniew ïa ki: u la sneng ïa ki syiem ruh namar jong ki;",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> u da ong, “Wat ktah ïa kiba la sleh jong nga, bad wat pynsniew ïa ki nongïathuhlypa jong nga.”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> To rwai ha U Trai, pha ka khyndew baroh; to pyni ïa ka jingpynim jong u man la ka sngi.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> To ïathuhkhana ïa ka burom jong u hapdeng ki jaid bynriew, ïa ki kam baphylla jong u hapdeng ki kynja bynriew baroh.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Naba u bakhraw long U Trai, bad ïa uba dei ïaroh eh: u long uba dei ruh ban sheptieng ïa u nalor ki blei baroh.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Naba ki blei baroh jong ki kynja bynriew ki long ki blei thala: hynrei, U Trai u la thaw ïa ki bneng.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Ka burom bad ka jinglong syiem ki long ha khmat jong u: ka bor bad ka jingsngewbha ki long ha ka jaka jong u.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> To ai ha U Trai, phi ki jaid ki jaid ki briew, ai ha U Trai, ka burom bad ka bor.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Ai ha U Trai, kata ka burom kaba dei ïa ka kyrteng jong u: to wallam ka jingainguh, bad to wan ha khmat jong u: mane ïa U Trai ha ka jingitynnad ka jingkhuid.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> To sngewtriem ha khmat jong u, pha ka khyndew baroh: ïa ka pyrthei ruh la pynskhem katba ym lah pynkhih ïa ka.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> To ki bneng kin kmen, bad ka khyndew to kan shadkmen; bad to kin ong hapdeng ki jaid bynriew, “U Trai u synshar.”",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> To ka duriaw kan kyrhuh, bad ka jingdap jong ka; to kan risa ka lyngkha, bad baroh katba don ha ka;",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> ynda kumta, ki dieng ha khlaw kin rwai da kaba kmen ha khmat U Trai, naba u wan ban bishar ïa ka khyndew.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> A to ainguh ha U Trai; naba u long u babha; namar ka jingisynei jong u ka ïaineh junom.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Bad to ong phi: “To pynim ïa ngi, A U Blei ka jingpynim jong ngi, bad to lum lang ïa ngi bad pyllait ïa ngi na ki jaid bynriew, ban ainguh ïa ka kyrteng bakhuid jong me, bad ban leh risa ha ka jingïaroh jong me.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> To long ba la kyrkhu ïa U Trai, U Blei ki Israel, naduh bymjukut shaduh bymjukut.” Bad u paidbah baroh u la ong, “Amen,” bad ki la ïaroh ïa U Trai.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Kumta, u la pynsah hangta, ha khmat ka synduk ka jutang U Trai, ïa u Asaph bad ki para jong u, ban shakri ha khmat ka synduk ka jutang borabor, katba donkam shi sngi shi sngi:",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> bad ïa u Obed-edom lem bad ki para jong ki, hynriewphew phra ngut; ïa u Obed-edom ruh u khun u Jeduthun bad u Hosah ban long ki nongap jingkhang:",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> bad ïa u Sadok u lyngdoh, bad ki para jong u ki lyngdoh, ha khmat Ka Tabernakl U Trai ha ka jaka bajrong kaba ha Gibeon,",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> ban ainguh ïa ki jingainguh thang ha U Trai halor ka duwan ka jingainguh thang borabor mynstep bad janmiet, katba kum kata baroh ba la thoh ha ka hukum U Trai, ïa kaba u la hukum ha ki Israel;",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> bad lem bad ki, ïa u Heman bad u Jeduthun, bad ïa kita kiwei pat ba la jied, kiba la khot da ka kyrteng, ban ainguh ha U Trai, naba ka jingisynei jong u ka neh ha la ka rta;",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> bad lem bad ki, u Heman bad u Jeduthun lem bad ki turoi bad ki 'sing padiah na ka bynta kita ki ban pynsawa jam, bad ki jingtem ïa ki jingrwai jong U Blei: bad ïa ki khun u Jeduthun ban long ha ka khyrdop.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Te u paidbah baroh ki la ïaleit noh uwei pa uwei sha la ïing la ïing: bad u Dabid u la leit phai ban kyrkhu ïa la ka ïing."
		},
		"17": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te katba u Dabid u la shong ha la ïing, u Dabid u la ong ha u Nathan u nongïathuhlypa, “Ha khmih, ma nga, nga shong hapoh ka ïing dieng Kedar, hynrei, ka synduk ka jutang U Trai ka shong hapoh ki pyrda.”",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te u Nathan u la ong ha u Dabid, “To leh ïa kata baroh kaba ha ka dohnud jong me; naba U Blei u long lem bad me.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te ha kata kajuh ka miet, ka ktien U Blei ka la wan ha u Nathan, ka da ong,",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> “Khie leit ïathuh ha u Dabid u shakri jong nga, ‘Kumne u ong U Trai, Men ym ïoh tei ka ïing ïa nga ban shong ha ka:",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> naba ngam shym la shong hapoh ka ïing naduh kata ka sngi ba nga la wallam noh ïa ki Israel, haduh kane ka sngi; hynrei, nga la leit na ka ïingjaiñ sha ka ïingjaiñ, bad na kawei Ka Tabernakl sha kawei pat.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ha ki jaka baroh ha kiba nga la ïaid lem bad ki Israel baroh, hato nga la kren shikyntien bad uno uno na ki nongbishar jong ki Israel, ïa kiba nga la hukum ban bsa ïa ki briew jong nga, ba nga ong, “Balei phim shym la tei ka ïing Kedar ïa nga?” ’",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Namar kata te, men ong ha u shakri jong nga u Dabid, ‘Kumne u ong U Trai ki paid, Nga la shim ïa me na ka sem langbrot, na kaba bud ïa ki langbrot, ba men long u nongïalam halor ki briew jong nga ki Israel:",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> bad nga la long lem bad me, kat shaba me la leit, bad nga la ot noh ïa ki nongshun jong me baroh na khmat jong me; bad ngan pynlong ha me ka nam, kaba kum ka nam jong ki bakhraw batri kiba don ha ka khyndew.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad ngan buh ka jaka ïa ki briew jong nga ki Israel, bad ngan thung ïa ki, ba kin ïoh shong ha la ka jong ka jaka, bad ba yn ym pynkhih shuh ïa ki; ki khun ka pop ruh kin ym pynjot shuh ïa ki, kum ha kaba nyngkong,",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> bad kumba naduh ka sngi ba nga la hukum ïa ki nongbishar ban long halor ki briew jong nga ki Israel; bad ngan pynhapoh ïa ki nongshun jong me baroh. Nalor kata ruh, nga ïathuh ha me ba U Trai un tei ïa me ka ïing.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te kan jia, haba ki sngi jong me ki la dap ba me dei ban ïaleit long lem bad ki kpa jong me, ba ngan pynïeng ïa u symbai jong me hadien jong me, u ban long na ki khun jong me; bad ngan pynskhem ïa ka hima jong u.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Uta, un tei ka ïing ïa nga, bad ngan pynskhem ïa ka khet jong u ha la ka rta.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ngan long u kpa jong u, bad un long u khun jong nga: bad ngan ym shim noh ïa ka jingisynei jong nga na u, kumba nga la shim na uta uba la long ha shuwa jong me:",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> hynrei, ngan pynneh skhem ïa u ha ka ïing jong nga bad ha ka hima jong nga ha la ka rta: bad ïa ka khet jong u yn pynskhem ha la ka rta.’ ”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Katba kum kine ki ktien baroh, bad katba kum kane ka jingithuhpaw baroh, kumta u Nathan u la kren ha u Dabid.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ynda kumta, u Dabid syiem u la leit bsut, bad u la shong ha khmat U Trai; bad u la ong, “Nga, nga long uei, A Trai U Blei, bad ka ïing jong nga ka long aïu, ba me la pynpoi ïa nga haduh katne?",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad kane ka la long kaba rit ha khmat jong me, A U Blei, hynrei, me la kren shaphang ka ïing u shakri jong me sha ka ban slem eh ruh, bad me la ñiew ïa nga katba kum ka jinglong jong u briew u bakhraw, A Trai U Blei.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Aïu pat u Dabid u lah ban dang ong shuh ha me shaphang ka burom ïa kaba la leh ha u shakri jong me? naba me ithuh ïa u shakri jong me.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> A Trai, na ka bynta u shakri jong me, bad katba kum ka dohnud jong me hi, me la leh ïa kane ka bakhraw baroh, ban pyntip ïa kine kiei kiei ki bakhraw baroh.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> A Trai, ym don uba kat ma me, lymne ym don U Blei nalor jong me, katba kum kata baroh ba ngi la ïohsngew da la ki shkor.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad kano kawei ka jaid bynriew ha ka khyndew kaba kum u paidlang jong me ki Israel, ïa kiba U Blei u la leit ban pynim ba kin long u paidlang ïa u hi, ban pynlong ïa me ka nam da kiei kiei kiba khraw bad kiba itriem, ha kaba beh noh ïa ki jaid bynriew na khmat ki briew jong me, ïa kiba me la pynim na Ijipt?",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Naba ïa ki briew jong me ki Israel, me la pynlong u paidlang la u jong hi ha la ka rta; bad ma me, A Trai, me la jia long U Blei jong ki.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te mynta, A Trai, kata ka ktien kaba me la kren shaphang u shakri jong me, bad shaphang ka ïing jong u, to kan long kaba skhem ha la ka rta, bad to leh kumba me la kren.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Bad to ai ba ka kyrteng jong me kan long ba la pynskhem bad ban pynkhraw ïa ka ha la ka rta, da kaba ong, ‘U Trai ki paid u long U Blei ki Israel, U Blei keiñ ha ki Israel:’ bad ïa ka ïing u Dabid u shakri jong me, la pynskhem ha khmat jong me.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Naba ma me, A U Blei jong nga, me la pynpaw ha u shakri jong me ba men tei ka ïing ïa u: namar kata, u shakri jong me u la shem ha la ka dohnud ban duwai ha khmat jong me.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Te mynta, A Trai, ma me, me long U Blei, bad me la kular ïa la u shakri ïa kane ka jingbha:",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> mynta te, me la sngewbha ban kyrkhu ïa ka ïing u shakri jong me, ba kan ïaisah ha la ka rta ha khmat jong me: naba ma me, A Trai, me la kyrkhu, bad ka long ba la kyrkhu ha la ka rta.”"
		},
		"18": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Hadien kane, u Dabid u la shoh ïa ki Philistia, bad u la jop ïa ki, bad u la knieh ïa ka Gath bad ki shnong jong ka na ka kti ki Philistia.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u la shoh ïa ki Moab; bad ki Moab ki la long ki khun kliarwait u Dabid, bad kiba ai khrong.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad u Dabid u la shoh ïa u Hadareser u syiem ka Sobah haduh Hamath, katba u la leit ban pynskhem ïa la ka hima harud ka wah Ïuphratis.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad u Dabid u la shim na u, shi hajar ki kali, bad hynñiew hajar ki nongshong kulai, bad arphew hajar kiba ïaleh na tbian: bad u Dabid u la ot ïa ki thied khohwah ki kulai ki kali ïapom baroh, hynrei, u la tyngkai na ki, shispah tylli ïa ki kali ïapom.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad haba ki Syria kiba na Damaskos ki la wan ban ïarap ïa u Hadareser u syiem ka Sobah, u Dabid u la pom arphew ar hajar ngut na ki Syria.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ynda kumta, u Dabid u la buh ki karod ha Syria Damaskos; bad kita ki Syria ki la long ki khun kliarwait ha u Dabid, bad kiba ai khrong. Bad U Trai u la ai ka jingjop ïa u Dabid kat shaba u la leit.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad u Dabid u la shim noh ïa ki stieh ksiar kiba ha ki shakri u Hadareser, bad u la wallam ïa ki sha Jerusalem.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad na Tibhath bad na Kun, ki nongbah u Hadareser, u Dabid u la shim shibun eh ka rnong, da kata, u Solomon u la shna ïa ka duriaw rnong, bad ïa ki rishot, bad ïa ki pliang rnong.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad haba u Tow u syiem ka Hamath u la ïohsngew ba u Dabid u la pom ïa ki paidïapom u Hadareser u syiem ka Sobah baroh,",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> u la phah ïa u Hadoram u khun jong u sha u syiem Dabid, ban khublei ïa u, bad ban kyrkhu ïa u, namar ba u la ïaleh thma bad u Hadareser bad ba u la shoh ïa u; naba u Hadareser u shait ïaleh thma ïa u Tow; bad u la don bad u ki jaid baroh ki pliang ksiar bad rupa bad rnong.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ïa kine ruh, u syiem Dabid u la pynkyntang ha U Trai, ryngkat bad ka rupa bad ka ksiar kaba u la kit noh na ki jaid bynriew baroh; na Edom, bad na Moab, bad na ki khun u Ammon, bad na ki Philistia, bad na ki Amalek.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad u Abishai u khun ka Seruïah ruh u la shoh na ki Edom ha ka Them Mluh, khatphra hajar.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad u la buh ki karod ha Edom; bad ki Edom baroh ki la long ki khun kliarwait ha u Dabid. Bad U Trai u la ai ka jingjop ïa u Dabid kat shaba u la leit.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad u Dabid u la synshar halor ki Israel baroh; bad u la leh ïa ka jingbishar bad ïa ka hok ha la ki briew baroh.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad u Joab u khun ka Seruïah, u la long halor ki paidïapom; bad u Jehoshaphat u khun u Ahilud, u la long u nongthoh rekord.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad u Sadok u khun u Ahitub, bad u Abimelekh u khun u Abiathar, ki la long lyngdoh; bad u Shabsha, u la long nongthoh;",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> bad u Benaïah u khun u Jehoïada, u la long halor ki Khereth bad ki Peleth; bad ki khun shynrang u Dabid ki la long rangbah bad u syiem."
		},
		"19": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad hadien kane, u Nahash u syiem ki khun u Ammon u la ïap, bad u khun jong u, u la synshar ha ka jaka jong u.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u Dabid u la ong, “Ngan leh sbun ïa u Hanun u khun u Nahash, namar u kpa jong u, u la leh sbun ïa nga.” Kumta, u Dabid u la phah ïa ki nonglam-ktien ban pyntngen ïa u na ka bynta u kpa jong u. Bad ki shakri u Dabid ki la wan sha ka ri ki khun u Ammon ha u Hanun, ban pyntngen ïa u.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Hynrei, ki rangbah ki khun u Ammon ki la ong ha u Hanun, “Me mut ba u Dabid u burom ïa u kpa jong me, ba u la phah ïa ki nongpyntngen ha me? Hato ki shakri jong u kim shym wan sha me ban jngoh, bad ban pynkyllon, bad ban syntiat ïa ka ri?”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Kumta, u Hanun u la shim ïa ki shakri u Dabid, bad u la khi ïa ki, bad u la khap noh ïa ki jaiñkup jong ki napdeng, haduh ki skhep jong ki, bad u la phah noh ïa ki.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te don kiba la leit ïathuh ha u Dabid kumno ba la leh ïa kita ki briew. Bad u la phah leit tan ïa ki; naba kita ki briew ki la lehrain shibun eh. Bad u syiem u la ong, “To sah ha Jerikho haduh ban da mih ki 'ñiuh tmoh jong phi, bad sa wan phai.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad haba ki khun u Ammon ki la ïohi ba ki la pynisih ïa lade ha u Dabid, u Hanun bad ki khun u Ammon ki la phah shi hajar talent ka rupa ban wer ïa ki, ki kali ïapom bad ki nongshong kulai na Mesopotamia, bad na Aram-maakah, bad na Sobah.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Kumta, ki la wer ïa ki laiphew ar hajar ki kali ïapom, bad ïa u syiem ka Maakah bad ki briew jong u; uba la wan bad u la sher dara ha khmat ka Madeba. Bad ki khun u Ammon ki la ïalum lang na ki nongbah jong ki, bad ki la wan ban ïaleh thma.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad haba u Dabid u la ïohsngew ïa kata, u la phah ïa u Joab, bad ïa ki paidïapom ki riewkhlaiñ bashlur baroh.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad ki khun u Ammon ki la mih noh, bad ki la ïabuh ryntih ïa ka thma ha ka khyrdop jong ka nongbah: bad ki syiem kiba la wan ki la long kyrpang hi ha madan.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Haba u Joab te u la ïohi ba la buh ïa ka thma pyrshah ïa u na sha khmat bad na shadien, u la jied na ki rangbah Israel ba la kynsai baroh, bad u la buh ryntih ïa ki, ban ïaleh ïa ki Syria.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad ïa kita kiwei na u paidbah u la aiti ha u Abishai u para jong u, bad ki la ïabuh ryntih ïa lade ban ïaleh ïa ki khun u Ammon.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad u la ong, “Lada ki Syria kin lah ïa nga, te men ïarap ïa nga: hynrei, lada ki khun u Ammon kin lah ïa me, nga te ngan ïarap ïa me.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> To long shlur, to ngin leh rangbah na ka bynta la ki briew, bad na ka bynta ki nongbah U Blei jong ngi: bad U Trai un leh ïa kata kaba u idei.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Kumta, u Joab bad uta u paid uba la don ryngkat bad u ki la tur hajan ha khmat ki Syria ban ïaleh thma ïa ki; bad ki la phet ïap ha khmat jong u.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad haba ki khun u Ammon ki la ïohi ba ki Syria ki la phet ïap, ki ruh ki la phet ïap ha khmat u Abishai u para jong u, bad ki la rung hapoh ka nongbah. Ynda kumta, u Joab u la wan sha Jerusalem.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad haba ki Syria ki la ïohi ba la jop ïa ki ha khmat ki Israel, ki la phah ïa ki nonglam-ktien, bad ki la pynmih ïa ki Syria kiba la don sha shiliang ka Wah, ryngkat bad u Shophakh u kaptan u paidïapom u Hadareser ha khlieh jong ki.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad la ïathuh ïa kata ha u Dabid: bad u la ïalum khar paid ïa ki Israel baroh, bad u la leit sha shiliang ka Jordan, bad u la lap ïa ki, bad u la buh pynbeit ïa ka thma ban ïaleh ïa ki. Kumta, u Dabid ynda u la buh pynbeit ban ïaleh ïa ki Syria, ki la ïaleh bad u.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad ki Syria ki la phet ïap ha khmat ki Israel; bad u Dabid u la pynïap na ki Syria ki rangbah hynñiew hajar ki kali ïapom, bad sawphew hajar kiba ïaleh na tbian, bad u la pynïap ïa u Shophakh u kaptan u paidïapom.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad haba ki shakri u Hadareser ki la ïohi ba la jop ïa ki ha khmat ki Israel, ki la ïasuk bad u Dabid, bad ki la shakri ïa u: ki Syria kim treh shuh ban ïarap ïa ki khun u Ammon."
		},
		"20": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te ha kawei pat ka snem, ha ka aïom ba ki syiem ki ju leit mih ban ïaleh thma, u Joab u la ïalam ïa u paidïapom bakynsai baroh, bad u la pynjot ïa ka ri ki khun u Ammon, bad u la wan ker kut ïa ka Rabbah. Hynrei, u Dabid u la sah ha Jerusalem. Bad u Joab u la shoh tangon ïa ka Rabbah, bad u la pynkyllon ïa ka.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u Dabid u la shim ïa ka pansngiat u syiem jong ki na ka khlieh jong u, bad u la shem ba ka khia shi talent ka ksiar, bad la don ki mawkordor ha ka; bad la buh ïa ka ha ka khlieh u Dabid: bad u la pynmih noh ïa ka jinglute jong ka shnong shibun eh.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad u la pynmih ïa ki briew kiba la don ha ka, bad u la ot ïa ki da ki kurat, bad da ki nar puh, bad ki sdie. Bad kumta u Dabid u la leh ïa ki shnong ki khun u Ammon baroh. Te u Dabid bad u paidbah baroh ki la leit phai pat sha Jerusalem.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te hadien kane, la mih ka thma bad ki Philistia ha Geser: te u Sibbekai u nong Hushath u la pynïap ïa u Sippai, uba na ki khun u riewradbah: bad la jop ïa ki.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad la long ka thma pat bad ki Philistia; bad u Elhanan u khun u Jair u la pynïap ïa u Lahmi u para u Goliath u nong Gitt, uba u dieng sum jong u kum u khung u nongthain jaiñ.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> La don pat ka thma ha Gath, ha kaba la don u briew uba heh met, uba ki shynriah'ti bad ki shynriah'jat jong u ki la long arphew saw tylli, hynriew tylli ha kawei kawei ka kti, bad hynriew tylli ha kawei kawei ka kjat; bad ïa u ruh la kha na u riewradbah.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te haba u la beiñ ïa ki Israel, u Jonathan u khun u Shimeah u hynmen u Dabid u la pynïap ïa u.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ïa kine la kha ha u riewradbah ha Gath; bad ki la kyllon da ka kti u Dabid, bad da ka kti ki shakri jong u."
		},
		"21": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te u Soitan u la ïeng ïaleh ïa ki Israel, bad u la pynkhih ïa u Dabid ban kheiñ ïa ki Israel.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u Dabid u la ong ha u Joab bad ha ki rangbah jong u paidbah, “Khie, da kheiñ ïa ki Israel naduh Beer-sheba haduh Dan; bad wallam ktien ha nga, ba ngan ïoh tip ïa ka jingkheiñ jong ki.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te u Joab u la ong, “To U Trai un pynlong ïa la u paidlang shispah shah shuh ïa kaba ki long: hynrei, ko kynrad u syiem, hato kim long baroh ki shakri u kynrad jong nga? Balei u kynrad jong nga u pan kum ïa kane? Balei un long ka daw ka jingbit pop ha ki Israel?”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> La kumta ruh, ka la kham lah ka ktien u syiem ban ïa u Joab. Namar kata, u Joab u la leit noh, bad u la leit lyngba ka Israel baroh, bad u la wan sha Jerusalem.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad u Joab u la aiti ïa ka jingkheiñ lang ïa u paidbah ha u Dabid. Bad ki Israel baroh ki la long shi hajar hajar bad shispah hajar kiba rah waitlam: bad ki Judah ki la long sawspah hynñiewphew hajar kiba rah waitlam.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Hynrei, ïa ki Lebi bad ïa ki Benjamin um shym la kheiñ hapdeng jong ki: namar ka ktien u syiem ka la long kaba isih ha u Joab.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad U Blei u la sngewsih ïa kane ka kam; namar kata, u la shoh tangon ïa ki Israel.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad u Dabid u la ong ha U Blei, “Nga la leh pop shibun eh, ha kaba nga la leh ïa kane ka kam: hynrei, mynta, nga kyrpad ïa me, to pyndam noh ïa ka jingleh bymhok u shakri jong me; namar nga la leh bieit shibun eh.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te U Trai u la kren ha u Gad, u nongïohi jong u Dabid, u da ong,",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> “Khie leit kren ha u Dabid, to ong, ‘Kumne u ong U Trai, Nga buh ha khmat jong me lai tylli kiei kiei; to jied ha me kawei na ki, ba ngan leh ïa kata ha me.’ ”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Kumta, u Gad u la wan ha u Dabid, u la ong ha u, “Kumne u ong U Trai, ‘To shim katba me mon;",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> lane lai snem ka 'nemsniew; lane lai bnai ban pynjot ïa me ha khmat ki nongshun jong me, haba ka waitlam ki nongshun jong me ka lap ïa me; lane ka waitlam U Trai, ka jingïapkhlam lai sngi ha ka ri keiñ, bad u angel U Trai u ban pynjot ha ki phang Israel baroh.’ Mynta te, to pyrkhat da kaba kumno ngan phai ktien ha uta uba la phah ïa nga.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te u Dabid u la ong ha u Gad, “Nga pisa eh: to ngan hap te ha ka kti U Trai; namar ki jingisynei jong u kiba khraw eh: te wat ai ba ngan hap ha ka kti u briew.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Kumta, U Trai u la phah da ka jingïapkhlam ha Israel: te ki la ïap hynñiewphew hajar ngut ki briew.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad U Blei u la phah ïa u angel sha Jerusalem ban pynjot ïa ka: bad haba un sa pynjot noh, U Trai u la khmih, bad u la kylla-ka-bamut shaphang kane ka jingpynsniew, bad u la ong ha u angel uba pynjot, “Keiñ noh katto; to pynsangeh ïa la ka kti.” Bad u angel U Trai u la ïeng hajan ka kyntem u Ornan u nong Jebus.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te u Dabid u la khmied ïa la ki khmat, bad u la ïohi ïa uta u angel U Trai ba u ïeng hapdeng ka khyndew bad ka bneng, uba bat ka waitlam ba la sei ha la ka kti ba la kner halor ka Jerusalem. Ynda kumta, u Dabid bad ki tymmen basan, kiba la kup da ki jaiñ byrni, ki la hap dem la ki khmat.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad u Dabid u la ong ha U Blei, “Ym long ma nga uba la hukum ban kheiñ ïa u paidbah? dei ma nga keiñ uba la leh pop bad nga la leh bymman eh; hynrei, kine ki langbrot, ki la leh aïu kine? Nga kyrpad ïa me, A Trai U Blei jong nga, to ka kti jong me kan long halor jong nga, bad halor ka ïing u kpa jong nga; hynrei, ym halor une u paidbah jong me, ba kin ïapkhlam.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te u angel U Trai u la hukum ïa u Gad ban ong ha u Dabid, ba u Dabid un leit kiew, bad tei ka duwan ha U Trai ha ka kyntem u Ornan u nong Jebus.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad u Dabid u la leit kiew ha ka jingong u Gad, kaba u la kren ha ka kyrteng U Trai.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te u Ornan u la kyrtiang, bad u la ïohi ïa u angel; bad ki saw ngut ki khun shynrang jong u kiba la don lem bad u ki la buhrieh ïa lade. Te u Ornan u dang shoh kba.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad katba u Dabid u la wan ha u Ornan, u Ornan u la khmih bad u la ïohi ïa u Dabid, bad u la mih noh na ka kyntem, bad u la dem ngon ïa lade ha u Dabid bad la ka khmat sha ka khyndew.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te u Dabid u la ong ha u Ornan, “To ai ha nga ïa ka jaka jong kane ka kyntem, ba ngan tei duwan ha ka ïa U Trai: men ai ïa ka ha nga ha ka dor babiang: khnang ban pynsangeh ïa ka jingïapkhlam na u paidbah.”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te u Ornan u la ong ha u Dabid, “To shim ha me, bad to u kynrad jong nga u syiem un leh katba ibit ha ki khmat jong u: ha khmih, nga ai ïa me ïa ki masi dab ban long ki jingainguh thang, bad ki tiar shoh kba ban long ki diengïap, bad u Kew ban long ka jingainguh bam; nga ai ïa ka baroh.”",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Te u syiem Dabid u la ong ha u Ornan, “Em; hynrei, ngan thied hi keiñ ïa ka da ka dor babiang: namar ngan ym shim ei ïa ka jong me ïa U Trai, lane ainguh ki jingainguh thang kiba shu ïoh ei.”",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Kumta, u Dabid u la ai ha u Ornan hynriewspah shekel ka ksiar da ka jingthew ïa kata ka jaka.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Bad u Dabid u la tei ïa ka duwan hangta ïa U Trai, bad u la ainguh ïa ki jingainguh thang bad ki jingainguh bapynïasuk, bad u la khot kyrpad ïa U Trai; U ruh U la phai ktien da ka ding na bneng halor ka duwan ka jingainguh thang.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Bad U Trai u la hukum ïa uta u angel; u ruh u la thep pat ïa la ka waitlam ha ka jingsop jong ka.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Ha kata ka por, haba u Dabid u la ïohi ba U Trai u la phai ktien ha ka kyntem u Ornan u nong Jebus, te u la kñia hangta.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Namar Ka Tabernakl U Trai, kaba u Moses u la thaw ha ka ri khlaw, bad ka duwan ka jingainguh thang, ki la don ha kata ka por ha ka jaka bajrong ha Gibeon.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Hynrei, u Dabid um lah ban leit ha khmat jong ka ban ïakylli na U Blei: naba u la sheptieng ïa ka waitlam u angel U Trai."
		},
		"22": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te u Dabid u la ong, “Kane ka long ka ïing U Trai U Blei, bad kane ka long ka duwan jingainguh thang ïa ki Israel.”",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u Dabid u la hukum ban ïalum lang ïa ki nongwei kiba la don ha ka ri Israel; bad u la thung ki misteri maw ban shtah ïa ki mawshtah ïa ka ban tei ïa ka ïing U Blei.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad u Dabid u la taïar kyrhai ka nar ban long prek ïa ki jingkhang khyrdop, bad ïa ki jingpyndait; bad kyrhai ka rnong kaba ym lah thew shuh:",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> bad ki dieng Kedar bym lah ñiew shuh: namar ki Sidon bad kiba na Tyros ki la wallam kyrhai ki dieng Kedar ha u Dabid.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad u Dabid u la ong, “U Solomon u khun jong nga u dang samla bad u dang lung ka met, bad kata ka ïing ka ban thaw ïa U Trai kan long kaba khraw shibun eh, kaba donnam donburom ha ki ri baroh sawdong: namar kata, ngan khreh hi ïa ka.” Kumta, u Dabid u la taïar kyrhai katba um pat ïap.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ynda kumta, u la khot ïa u Solomon u khun jong u, bad u la hukum ïa u ban tei ka ïing ïa U Trai, U Blei ki Israel.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad u Dabid u la ong ha u Solomon u khun jong u, “Ha nga hi, ka la don ha ka dohnud jong nga ban thaw ka ïing ïa ka kyrteng U Trai U Blei jong nga.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Hynrei, ka ktien U Trai ka la wan ha nga, ka da ong, ‘Me la pynmih snam shibun eh, bad me la pynlong ki thma ki bakhraw: men ym ïohthaw ka ïing ma me ïa ka kyrteng jong nga, namar me la pynmih shibun ka snam halor ka khyndew ha khmat jong nga:",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> ha khmih, yn kha u khun ïa me, u ban long u briew ka jingsuk; bad ngan ai ïa u ka jingshongthait na ki nongshun jong u baroh sawdong: namar ka kyrteng jong u kan long “u Solomon”, bad ngan ai ka jingsuk bad ka jingjai jai ha Israel ha ki sngi jong u:",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> u, un tei ka ïing ïa ka kyrteng jong nga; bad, u, un long u khun jong nga, bad nga ruh ngan long u kpa jong u; bad ngan pynskhem ïa ka khet ka hima jong u halor ki Israel ha la ka rta.’ ”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> “Te, ko khun, U Trai un long ryngkat bad me; bad to man bha, bad to tei ïa kata ka ïing U Trai U Blei jong me, kumba u la kren shaphang jong me.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Tangba U Trai un ai ïa me ka jingsian bad ka jingsngewthuh, bad ba un ai ha me ka hukum shaphang ki Israel; ba kumta, men ïoh sumar ïa ka hukum U Trai U Blei jong me.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te men man bha, lada me sumar ban leh ïa ki aiñ bad ki jingbishar kiba U Trai u la hukum ïa u Moses shaphang ki Israel: to long u bakhlaiñ, bad uba shlur bha; wat sheptieng, lymne sngewkyiuh.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te ha khmih, ha ka jingshitom jong nga, nga la taïar na ka bynta ka ïing U Trai shispah hajar talent ka ksiar, bad hajar hajar talent ka rupa; bad ïa ka rnong bad ka nar ka bym lah thew shuh; namar ka bun than eh: ki dieng bad u maw ruh nga la taïar; bad me ruh me lah ban nang pynbun shuh shuh.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Nalor kata, me don kyrhai ki nongtrei, ki nongshtah bad ki nongtrei maw bad dieng, bad baroh ki briew kiba nang ha kano kano ka rukom jingtrei;",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> shaphang ka ksiar, ka rupa, bad ka rnong, bad ka nar ruh, ym don jingkheiñ; to ïeng bad to trei, bad U Trai un long ryngkat bad me.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> U Dabid u la hukum ruh ïa ki rangbah Israel baroh ba kin ïarap ïa u Solomon u khun jong u, u da ong,",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> “Hato U Trai U Blei jong phi um don ryngkat bad phi? Bad um shym la ai ka jingshongthait ïa phi baroh sawdong? Namar u la aiti ïa ki briew jong ka ri ha nga; bad ïa kata ka ri la jop ha khmat U Trai, bad ha khmat ki briew jong u.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Mynta te, to thew ha la ka dohnud bad la ka mynsiem ban wad ïa U Trai U Blei jong phi; to ïeng namar kata, bad to phin ïatei ïa ka jaka kyntang jong U Trai U Blei, ban wallam ïa ka synduk ka jutang U Trai, bad ïa ki pliang bakhuid U Blei, hapoh ka ïing ka ban sa thaw ha ka kyrteng U Trai.”"
		},
		"23": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te u Dabid u la tymmen bad ki sngi jong u ki la dap; bad u la thung syiem ïa u Solomon u khun jong u halor ki Israel.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u la ïalum lang ïa ki rangbah Israel baroh, lem bad ki lyngdoh bad ki Lebi de.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad ïa ki Lebi la kheiñ naduh kiba laiphew snem artet: bad ka jingkheiñ jong ki marwei marwei, uwei pa uwei, ka la long laiphew phra hajar ngut.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> “Na kine, arphew saw hajar ki ban khmih ïa ka kam ka ïing U Trai; bad hynriew hajar ki la long ki rangbah bad ki nongbishar.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad saw hajar ki la long ki nongap jingkhang; bad saw hajar ki la ïaroh ïa U Trai da ki jingtem kiba nga la thaw,” u Dabid u la ong, “ban ïaroh da kita.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te u Dabid u la pynïabynta ïa ki ha ki jingkylliang katba kum ki khun u Lebi: u Gershon, u Kohath, bad u Merari.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na ki Gershon: u Ladan bad u Shimei.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ki khun shynrang u Ladan: u Jehiel u rangbah, bad u Setham, bad u Joel, lai ngut.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ki khun shynrang u Shimei: u Shelomoth, bad u Hasiel, bad u Haran, lai ngut. Kine ki la long ki rangbah ki ïing ki kpa na u Ladan.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Shimei: u Jahath, u Sina, bad u Jeush, bad u Beriah. Kine saw ngut ki la long ki khun u Shimei.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> U Jahath u la long u rangbah, bad u Sisah uba bud: hynrei, u Jeush bad u Beriah kim don shibun ki khun shynrang; namar kata, ki la long ka ïing ki kpa da kaba kheiñ lang ïa ki.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ki khun shynrang u Kohath: u Amram, u Ishar, u Hebron, bad u Ussiel, saw ngut.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ki khun shynrang u Amram: u Aaron bad u Moses: te ïa u Aaron la pynkyrpang, ba un pynkyntang ïa kiei kiei ki bakyntang tam, ma u bad ki khun jong u, ha la ka rta, ban thang jingiwbih ha khmat U Trai, ban shakri ha U, bad ban kyrkhu ha ka kyrteng jong U, ha la ka rta.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Hynrei, shaphang u Moses u briew jong U Blei, ïa ki khun shynrang jong u la kyrteng lang hapdeng ka jaid Lebi.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ki khun shynrang u Moses: u Gershom bad u Elieser.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ki khun shynrang u Gershom: u Shebuel u rangbah.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ki khun shynrang u Elieser ki la long, u Rehabiah u rangbah. Bad u Elieser um don kiwei pat ki khun shynrang; hynrei, ki khun shynrang u Rehabiah ki la don shibun.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ki khun shynrang u Ishar: u Shelomith u rangbah.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ki khun shynrang u Hebron: u Jeriah u rangbah, u Amariah uba bud, u Jahasiel u balai, bad u Jekamiam u basaw.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ki khun shynrang u Ussiel: u Mikah u rangbah, bad u Isshiah uba bud.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ki khun shynrang u Merari: u Mahli bad u Mushi. Ki khun shynrang u Mahli: u Eleasar, bad u Kish.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Bad u Eleasar u la ïap, bad um don khun shynrang, tang ki kynthei: bad ki para jong ki, ki khun u Kish ki la shongkurim ïa ki.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Ki khun shynrang u Mushi: u Mahli, bad u Eder, bad u Jeremoth, lai ngut.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Kine ki long ki khun shynrang u Lebi katba kum ki ïing ki kpa jong ki, ki rangbah keiñ ki ïing ki kpa jong kita ïa kiba la kheiñ, ha ka jingkheiñ ki kyrteng marwei marwei, kiba la trei ïa ka kam ïa ka jingshakri ha ka ïing U Trai, naduh kiba arphew snem ka rta artet.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Namar u Dabid u la ong, “U Trai, U Blei ki Israel, u la ai ka jingshongthait ha la ki briew; bad u shong ha Jerusalem ha la ka rta:",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> bad ki Lebi ruh kim donkam shuh ban ïakit ïa Ka Tabernakl bad ïa ki pliang jong ka baroh ïa ka jingshakri jong ka.”",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Namar da ki ktien ki bakhatduh jong u Dabid, ïa ki khun u Lebi la ñiew naduh kiba arphew snem ka rta artet.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> “Namar ka kam jong ki ka la long ban ïarap ïa ki khun u Aaron ïa ka jingshakri ha ka ïing U Trai, ha ki phyllaw, bad ha ki kamra, bad ha kaba pynkhuid ïa kiei kiei baroh ki bakyntang, ka kam ka jingshakri ha ka ïing U Blei keiñ;",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> ïa u 'pu pyni ruh, bad ïa u 'purew bani ban long ka jingainguh bam, la ka jong ki 'pu stang bakhlem thiat, lane ka jong kita kiba shu syang ha ka nar sdieh, lane ka jong kiba shu wieh, bad ïa ka jaid baroh ka jingthew bad jingheh;",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> bad ban ïeng man la ka step ban ainguh bad ban ïaroh ïa U Trai, bad kumjuh janmiet de;",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> bad ban ainguh ïa ki jingainguh thang baroh ha U Trai, ha ki Sabbaton, ha ki 'nai thymmai, bad ha Ki Jingkhawai Niam ba la buh, ha ka jingñiew katba kum ka rukom shaphang jong ki, ha la ka sngi ha khmat U Trai:",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> bad ba kin ïa-ap ïa ka ïingjaiñ ka jingïaseng, bad ïa ka jaka kyntang, bad ïa ki khun u Aaron ki para jong ki, ïa ka jingshakri ka ïing U Trai.”"
		},
		"24": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te kine ki long ki jingkylliang ki khun shynrang u Aaron. Ki khun u Aaron: u Nadab bad u Abihu, u Eleasar bad u Ithamar.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Hynrei, u Nadab bad u Abihu ki la ïap shuwa ïa u kpa jong ki, bad kim shym don khun; namar kata, u Eleasar bad u Ithamar ki la kam ïa ka kam lyngdoh.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad u Dabid lem bad u Sadok na ki khun u Eleasar, bad u Ahimelekh na ki khun u Ithamar, ki la ïabynta ïa ki katba kum ki jinglong jong ki ha la ki kam.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad la shem ba don kham bun ki rangbah na ki khun u Eleasar ban ïa na ki khun u Ithamar; bad kumne la pynbynta ïa ki: na ki khun u Eleasar la don khathynriew ngut ki rangbah ki ïing ki kpa; bad na ki khun u Ithamar phra ngut, katba kum ki ïing ki kpa jong ki.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Kumne la ïa-pynbynta ïa ki da ka jingkhalai, kawei ka jaid bad kawei pat; namar la don ki rangbah ka jaka kyntang, bad ki rangbah U Blei, na ki khun u Eleasar ruh, bad na ki khun u Ithamar.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad u Shemaïah u khun u Nethanil u nongthoh, uba na ki Lebi, u la thoh ïa ki ha khmat u syiem, bad ki rangbah, bad u Sadok u lyngdoh, bad u Ahimelekh u khun u Abiathar, bad ki rangbah ki ïing ki kpa na ki lyngdoh bad na ki Lebi: kawei ka ïing ki kpa la shim na ka bynta u Eleasar, bad kawei la shim na ka bynta u Ithamar.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te ka jingkhalai ka banyngkong ka la hap ha u Jehoïarib, ka ba-ar ha u Jedaïah;",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> ka balai ha u Harim, ka basaw ha u Seorim;",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> ka basan ha u Malkhijah, ka bahynriew ha u Mejamin;",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> ka bahynñiew ha u Hakkas, ka baphra ha u Abijah;",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> ka bakhyndai ha u Jeshua, ka bashiphew ha u Shekaniah;",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> ka bakhatwei ha u Eliashib, ka bakhat-ar ha u Jakim;",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> ka bakhatlai ha u Huppah, ka bakhatsaw ha u Jeshebeab;",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> ka bakhatsan ha u Bilgah, ka bakhathynriew ha u Immer;",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> ka bakhathynñiew ha u Hesir, ka bakhatphra ha u Happisses;",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> ka bakhatkhyndai ha u Pethahiah, ka ba-arphew ha u Jeheskel;",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> ka ba-arphew wei ha u Jakhin, ka ba-arphew ar ha u Gamul;",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> ka ba-arphew lai ha u Delaïah, ka ba-arphew saw ha u Maasiah.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Kane ka long ka rukom jong ki ha la ka kam, ban wan sha ka ïing U Trai katba kum ka jingbuh rukom ba la ai ha ki da ka kti u Aaron u kpa jong ki, kumba U Trai, U Blei ki Israel, u la hukum ïa u.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad na kita kiwei ki khun u Lebi: na ki khun u Amram, u Shubael; na ki khun u Shubael, u Jehdeïah.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na u Rehabiah: na ki khun u Rehabiah, u Isshiah u rangbah.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na ki Ishar, u Shelomoth; na ki khun u Shelomoth, u Jahath.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Bad ki khun u Hebron: u Jeriah u rangbah, u ba-ar u Amariah, u balai u Jahasiel, u basaw u Jekameam:",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> ki khun u Ussiel, u Mikah; na ki khun u Mikah, u Shamir.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> U para u Mikah, u Isshiah: na ki khun u Isshiah, u Sekharaïah.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Ki khun u Merari: u Mahli bad u Mushi; ki khun u Jaasiah: u Beno.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Ki khun u Merari; na ki jong u Jaasiah, u Beno, bad u Shoham, bad u Sakkur, bad u Ibri.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Na ki jong u Mahli: u Eleasar, u bymdon khun shynrang.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Na ki jong u Kish: ki khun shynrang u Kish, u Jerahmil.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Mushi: u Mahli, bad u Eder, bad u Jerimoth. Kine ki long ki khun shynrang ki Lebi katba kum ki ïing ki kpa jong ki.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Kine ruh ki la noh ka jingkhalai kum ki khun shynrang u Aaron ki para jong ki ha khmat u Dabid u syiem, bad u Sadok, bad u Ahimelekh, bad ki rangbah ki ïing ki kpa na ki lyngdoh bad na ki Lebi; ki ïing ki kpa jong u rangbah kumjuh kum ki jong u para uba kham rit."
		},
		"25": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Nalor kata, u Dabid bad ki kaptan u paidïapom ki la pynkyrpang katto katne na ki khun shynrang u Asaph, bad na ki jong u Heman, bad na ki jong u Jeduthun, na ka bynta ka kam, ki ban ïathuhlypa da ki duitara, da ki nebel, bad da ki 'sing padiah: bad ka jingkheiñ kita kiba trei ïa ka kam ha la ka kam ka kam ka la long:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> na ki khun shynrang u Asaph: u Sakkur, bad u Joseph, bad u Nethaniah, bad u Asharelah, ki khun shynrang u Asaph; hapoh ka kti u Asaph, kiba la ïathuhlypa kat kum ka hukum u syiem.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na u Jeduthun: ki khun shynrang u Jeduthun: u Gedalaïah, bad u Seri, u Jeshaïah, u Hashabiah, bad u Mattithiah, hynriew ngut; hapoh ka kti u kpa jong ki, u Jeduthun lem bad ka duitara, uba ïathuhlypa ha ki jingainguh bad ha kaba ïaroh ïa U Trai.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na u Heman, ki khun shynrang u Heman: u Bukkiah, u Mattaniah, u Ussiel, u Shebuel, bad u Jerimoth, u Hananiah, u Hanani, u Eliathah, u Giddalti, bad u Romamti-eser, u Joshbekashah, u Mallothi, u Hothir, u Mahasioth:",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> kine baroh ki long ki khun shynrang u Heman u nongïohi u syiem ha ki ktien U Blei, ban kyntiew ïa ka reng. Bad U Blei u la ai ïa u Heman khatsaw ngut ki khun shynrang bad lai ngut ki khun kynthei.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Kine baroh ki long hapoh ka kti u kpa jong ki na ka bynta ka jingrwai ha ka ïing U Trai, lem bad ki 'sing padiah, ki nebel, bad ki duitara, na ka bynta ka kam ka ïing U Blei; u Asaph, u Jeduthun, bad u Heman ki long hapoh ka hukum u syiem.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad ka jingkheiñ jong ki, lem bad ki para jong ki kiba la hikai ïa ka ban rwai ha U Trai, baroh keiñ kiba la nang, ka la long arspah phraphew phra.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad ki la noh ki jingkhalai ïa la ka jong ka jong ka jingsumar, baroh kumjuh, uba rit ruh bad uba khraw, u nonghikai ruh bad uba shah hikai.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te ka jingkhalai ka banyngkong ka la hap ha u Joseph na ka bynta u Asaph: ka ba-ar ha u Gedalaïah; ma u bad la ki para bad la ki khun shynrang ki la long khat-ar ngut:",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> ka balai ha u Sakkur, ki khun shynrang bad ki para jong u, khat-ar ngut:",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> ka basaw ha u Isri, ki khun shynrang bad ki para jong u, khat-ar ngut:",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> ka basan ha u Nethaniah, ki khun shynrang bad ki para jong u, khat-ar ngut:",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> ka bahynriew ha u Bukkiah, ki khun shynrang bad ki para jong u, khat-ar ngut:",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> ka bahynñiew ha u Jesharelah, ki khun shynrang bad ki para jong u, khat-ar ngut:",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> ka baphra ha u Jeshaïah, ki khun shynrang bad ki para jong u, khat-ar ngut:",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> ka bakhyndai ha u Mattaniah, ki khun shynrang bad ki para jong u, khat-ar ngut:",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> ka bashiphew ha u Shimei, ki khun shynrang bad ki para jong u, khat-ar ngut:",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> ka bakhatwei ha u Asarel, ki khun shynrang bad ki para jong u, khat-ar ngut:",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> ka bakhat-ar ha u Hashabiah, ki khun shynrang bad ki para jong u, khat-ar ngut:",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> ka bakhatlai ha u Shubael, ki khun shynrang bad ki para jong u, khat-ar ngut:",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> ka bakhatsaw ha u Mattithiah, ki khun shynrang bad ki para jong u, khat-ar ngut:",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> ka bakhatsan ha u Jeremoth, ki khun shynrang bad ki para jong u, khat-ar ngut:",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> ka bakhathynriew ha u Hananiah, ki khun shynrang bad ki para jong u, khat-ar ngut:",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> ka bakhathynñiew ha u Joshbekashah, ki khun shynrang bad ki para jong u, khat-ar ngut:",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> ka bakhatphra ha u Hanani, ki khun shynrang bad ki para jong u, khat-ar ngut:",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> ka bakhatkhyndai ha u Mallothi, ki khun shynrang bad ki para jong u, khat-ar ngut:",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> ka ba-arphew ha u Eliathah, ki khun shynrang bad ki para jong u, khat-ar ngut:",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> ka ba-arphew wei ha u Hothir, ki khun shynrang bad ki para jong u, khat-ar ngut:",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> ka ba-arphew ar ha u Giddalti, ki khun shynrang bad ki para jong u, khat-ar ngut:",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> ka ba-arphew lai ha u Mahasioth, ki khun shynrang bad ki para jong u, khat-ar ngut:",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> ka ba-arphew saw ha u Romamti-eser, ki khun shynrang bad ki para jong u, khat-ar ngut."
		},
		"26": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na ka bynta ki jingkylliang ki nongap jingkhang: na ki Korah; u Meshelemiah u khun u Kore, na ki khun u Asaph.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u Meshelemiah u la don ki khun shynrang: u Sekharaïah u banyngkong, u Jediael u ba-ar, u Sebadaïah u balai, u Jathniel u basaw;",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> u Elam u basan, u Jehohanan u bahynriew, u Eliehoenai u bahynñiew.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad u Obed-edom u la don ki khun shynrang; u Shemaïah u banyngkong, u Jehosabad u ba-ar, u Joah u balai, bad u Sakar u basaw, bad u Nethanil u basan;",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> u Ammiel u bahynriew, u Issakhar u bahynñiew, u Peullethai u baphra: namar U Blei u la kyrkhu ïa u.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ïa u Shemaïah ruh u khun jong u la kha ki khun shynrang, kiba la synshar halor ka ïing u kpa jong ki: namar ki la long ki riewkhlaiñ bashlur.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ki khun u Shemaïah: u Othni bad u Rephael, bad u Obed, u Elsabad, kiba ki para jong ki, ki long kiba shynrang ki briew, u Elihu, bad u Semakhiah.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Kine baroh ki la long na ki khun u Obed-edom; ma ki bad ki khun shynrang jong ki bad ki para jong ki, ki briew ki bakhlaiñ ïa kata ka kam; hynriewphew ar ngut na u Obed-edom.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad u Meshelemiah u la don ki khun shynrang bad ki para, kiba shynrang ki briew, khatphra ngut.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> U Hosah ruh, na ki khun u Merari, u la don ki khun shynrang: u Shimri u rangbah, (namar la um shym long u khun nyngkong, pynban, u kpa jong u, u la pynlong rangbah ïa u:)",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> u Hilkiah u ba-ar, u Tebaliah u balai, u Sekharaïah u basaw: baroh ki khun shynrang bad ki para u Hosah ki la long khatlai ngut.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na kine la long ki jingkylliang ki nongap jingkhang, na ki rangbah keiñ, kiba don ki jingsumar kumjuh kum ki para jong ki, ban shakri ha ka ïing U Trai.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad ki la pynnoh ïa ki jingkhalai, ïa kiba rit ruh bad ïa kiba khraw, katba kum ki ïing ki kpa jong ki, ïa kawei pa kawei ka khyrdop.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad ka bynta ba shaphang mihngi ka la hap ha u Shelemiah. Hadien kata, ïa u Sekharaïah u khun jong u, u myntri u bastad, ki la pynnoh ïa ki jingkhalai; bad ka bynta jong u ka la hap shaphang shatei.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ïa u Obed-edom shaphang shathie; bad ïa ki khun jong u ka ïing jingkynshew.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ïa u Shuppim bad u Hosah shaphang sepngi, hajan ka khyrdop Shallekheth, ha ka lynti bah kaba kiew artet, ka jingap pyrshah ïa ka jingap.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Shaphang mihngi la don hynriew ngut ki Lebi, shaphang shatei saw ngut shi sngi shi sngi, shaphang shathie saw ngut shi sngi shi sngi, bad ïa ka ïing jingkynshew ar ngut ar ngut.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ïa ka Parbar shaphang sepngi, saw ngut ha lynti bah, bad ar ngut ha ka Parbar.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Kine ki la long ki jingkylliang ki nongap jingkhang; na ki khun u Korah, bad na ki khun u Merari.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad na ki Lebi, u Ahijah u la long halor ki jingkynshew ka ïing U Blei, bad halor ki jingkynshew jong kiei kiei ba la kyntang.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ki khun u Ladan; ki khun ki Gershon kiba dei ïa u Ladan, ki rangbah ki ïing ki kpa kiba dei ïa u Ladan u nong Gershon: u Jehieli.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ki khun shynrang u Jehieli: u Setham, bad u Joel u para jong u, halor ki jingkynshew ka ïing U Trai.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na ki Amram, na ki Ishar, na ki Hebron, na ki Ussiel:",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> bad u Shebuel u khun u Gershom, u khun u Moses, u la long nongsynshar halor ki jingkynshew.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bad ki para jong u; na u Elieser la wan u Rehabiah u khun jong u, bad u Jeshiah u khun jong u, bad u Joram u khun jong u, bad u Sikhri u khun jong u, bad u Shelomoth u khun jong u.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Une u Shelomoth bad ki para jong u ki la long halor ki jingkynshew baroh jong kiei kiei ba la kyntang, ïa kiba u Dabid u syiem, bad ki rangbah ki ïing ki kpa, ki kaptan halor ki hajar bad halor ki spah, bad ki kaptan ki paidïapom, ki la pynkyntang.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Na ka jinglute ba la ïoh ha ki thma ki la pynkyntang ban shna pat ïa ka ïing U Trai.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Bad baroh ïa kaba u Samuel u nongïohi, bad u Saul u khun u Kish, bad u Abner u khun u Ner, bad u Joab u khun ka Seruïah, ki la pynkyntang; uno uno uba la pynkyntang ïa kaei kaei, ka la long ha ka kti u Shelomoth, bad ki para jong u.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Na ki Ishar, u Khenaniah bad ki khun shynrang jong u ki la long halor ki Israel ïa ki kam kiba shabar, ban long ki rangbah bad ki nongbishar.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Na ki Hebron, u Hashabiah bad ki para jong u, ki briew bashlur, shi hajar hynñiewspah, ki la khmih sumar ïa ki Israel sha shiliang ka Jordan shaphang sepngi; ïa ka kam U Trai baroh, bad ïa ka kam u syiem.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Na ki Hebron u Jerijah u la long rangbah, na ki Hebron keiñ, katba kum ka jinghiar pateng jong ki da ki ïing ki kpa. Ha ka snem ka basawphew ka jingsynshar u Dabid la wad ïa ki, bad la shem hapdeng jong ki, ïa ki riewkhlaiñ ki bashlur ha Jaser ka Gilead.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Bad ki para jong u, ki briew bashlur, ki la long ar hajar hynñiewspah, ki rangbah ki ïing ki kpa, ïa kiba u Dabid u syiem u la pynlong nongkhmih halor ki Reuben, bad ki Gad, bad ki shiteng ka jaid ki Manasseh, ïa ka kam baroh kaba dei ïa U Blei, bad ïa ki kam u syiem."
		},
		"27": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te ki khun Israel katba kum ka jingkheiñ jong ki, kata, ki rangbah ki ïing ki kpa, bad ki kaptan ki hajar bad ki spah, bad ki rangbah jong ki kiba shakri ïa u syiem, ha kano kano ka kam jong kita ki jingkylliang kiba rung bad kiba mih man la u bnai ha ki bnai baroh jong ka snem, ha kawei kawei ka jingkylliang, ki la long arphew saw hajar.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Halor ka jingkylliang ka banyngkong ïa u bnai u banyngkong, u la long u Jashobeam u khun u Sabdiel: bad ha ka jingkylliang jong u, ki la long arphew saw hajar.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> U la long na ki khun u Peres, u rangbah ki kaptan baroh ki paidïapom ïa u bnai banyngkong.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad halor ka jingkylliang ïa u bnai u ba-ar, u la long u Dodai u nong Ahohi, bad ka jingkylliang jong u; bad u Mikloth u nongsynshar: bad ha ka jingkylliang jong u, ki la long arphew saw hajar.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> U Kaptan u balai ïa ki paidïapom ïa u bnai u balai, u la long u Benaïah, u khun u Jehoïada u lyngdoh, u rangbah: bad ha ka jingkylliang jong u, ki la long arphew saw hajar.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Une u long uta u Benaïah, uba long u briew bakhlaiñ na ki laiphew ngut, bad uba halor ki laiphew ngut: bad na ka jingkylliang jong u, la long u Ammisabad u khun jong u.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> U Kaptan u basaw ïa u bnai u basaw, u la long u Asahel u para u Joab, bad u Sebadiah u khun jong u hadien jong u: bad ha ka jingkylliang jong u, ki la long arphew saw hajar.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> U kaptan u basan ïa u bnai u basan, u la long u Shamhuth u nong Israh: bad ha ka jingkylliang jong u, ki la long arphew saw hajar.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> U kaptan u bahynriew ïa u bnai u bahynriew, u la long u Ira u khun u Ikkesh u nong Tekoa; bad ha ka jingkylliang jong u, ki la long arphew saw hajar.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> U kaptan u bahynñiew ïa u bnai u bahynñiew, u la long u Heles u nong Pelon, na ki khun u Ephraim: bad ha ka jingkylliang jong u, ki la long arphew saw hajar.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> U kaptan u baphra ïa u bnai u baphra, u la long u Sibbekai u nong Hushah, na ki nong Serah: bad ha ka jingkylliang jong u, ki la long arphew saw hajar.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> U kaptan u bakhyndai ïa u bnai u bakhyndai, u la long u Abieser u nong Anathoth, na ki Benjamin: bad ha ka jingkylliang jong u, ki la long arphew saw hajar.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> U kaptan u bashiphew ïa u bnai u bashiphew, u la long u Maharai u nong Netophath, na ki nong Serah: bad ha ka jingkylliang jong u, ki la long arphew saw hajar.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> U kaptan u bakhatwei ïa u bnai u bakhatwei, u la long u Benaïah u nong Pirathon, na ki khun u Ephraim: bad ha ka jingkylliang jong u, ki la long arphew saw hajar.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> U kaptan u bakhat-ar ïa u bnai u bakhat-ar, u la long u Heldai u nong Netophath, na u Othniel: bad ha ka jingkylliang jong u, ki la long arphew saw hajar.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Nalor kata, halor ki jaid Israel: na ki Reuben, u Elieser u khun u Sikhri u la long u nongsynshar: na ki Simeon, u Shephatiah u khun u Maakah:",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> na u Lebi, u Hashabiah u khun u Kemuel: na u Aaron, u Sadok:",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> na u Judah, u Elihu, uwei na ki hynmen u Dabid: na u Issakhar, u Omri u khun u Mikhael:",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> na u Sabulon, u Ishmaïah u khun u Obadaïah: na u Naphtali, u Jerimoth u khun u Asriel:",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> na ki khun u Ephraim, u Hoshea u khun u Asasiah: na ka shiteng ka jaid u Manasseh, u Joel u khun u Pedaïah:",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> na shiteng ka jaid u Manasseh ha Gilead, u Iddo u khun u Sekharaïah: na u Benjamin, u Jaasiel u khun u Abner:",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> na u Dan, u Asarel u khun u Jeroham. Kine ki la long ki kaptan ïa ki jaid Israel.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Hynrei, u Dabid um shym shim jingkheiñ ïa ki naduh kiba arphew snem ka rta bad kiba hapoh: namar U Trai u la ong ba un pynroi ïa ki Israel kum ki khlur ka bneng.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> U Joab u khun ka Seruïah u la sdang ban ñiew, hynrei, um shym dep; bad namar kane, la wan ka jingbitar halor ki Israel; lymne ym shym thoh ïa kata ka jingkheiñ ha ka jingïathuh ha Ki Khronikl u syiem Dabid.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bad halor ki jingkynshew u syiem, u la long u Asmabeth u khun u Adiel: bad halor ki jingkynshew ha ki lyngkha, ha ki nongbah, bad ha ki nongrit, bad ha ki kut, u la long u Jonathan u khun u Ussiah:",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> bad halor kita kiba trei ïa ka lyngkha ban rep ïa ka khyndew, u la long u Esri u khun u Khelub:",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> bad halor ki brisoh, u la long u Shimei u nong Ramath: bad halor ka jingmih ki brisoh na ka bynta ki kamra khrum buh Waiñ, u la long u Sabdi u nong Shiphmi:",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> bad halor ki dieng Olib bad ki dieng Dumbur kiba long ha them, u la long u Baal-hanan u nong Geder: bad halor ki kamra khrum buh umphniang, u la long u Joash:",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> bad halor ki kynhun masi kiba bam phlang ha Sharon, u la long u Shitrai u nong Sharon: bad halor ki kynhun masi kiba don ha ki them, u la long u Shaphat u khun u Adlai:",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> bad halor ki ut, u la long u Obil u kynja Ishmael: bad halor ki kadda, u la long u Jehdeïah u nong Meronoth:",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> bad halor ki kynhun langbrot, u la long u Jasis u nong Hager. Kine baroh ki la long ki nongsynshar ïa ka spah kaba la long ka jong u syiem Dabid.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> U Jonathan ruh, u kñi u Dabid u la long u myntri, u briew u bashemphang bad u nongthoh: bad u Jehiel u khun u Hakhmoni u la long lem bad ki khun syiem:",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> bad u Ahithophel u la long u myntri u syiem: bad u Hushai u nong Arkhi u la long u lok u syiem:",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> bad hadien u Ahithophel la long u Jehoïada u khun u Benaïah, bad u Abiathar: bad u kaptan ki paidïapom u syiem, u la long u Joab."
		},
		"28": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te u Dabid u la lum lang ïa ki rangbah ki Israel baroh, ïa ki rangbah ki jaid, bad ki kaptan ki kynhun kiba shakri ïa u syiem da ka jingïakylliang, bad ki kaptan ki shi hajar, bad ki kaptan ki shispah, bad ki nongsynshar halor baroh ka spah bad ki jingdon jong u syiem bad ki jong ki khun jong u, lem bad ki ïunukh, bad ki riewkhraw bor, baroh keiñ ki riewkhlaiñ bashlur, ha Jerusalem.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ynda kumta, u Dabid u syiem u la ïeng joit da la ki kjat, bad u la ong, “To sngap ïa nga, ko para, bad ki briew jong nga: ma nga te, ka la don ha ka dohnud jong nga ban tei ka ïing shongthait ïa ka synduk ka jutang U Trai, bad ban long ka jingïuh kjat jong U Blei jong ngi; bad nga la lah khreh khnang ïa ka jingtei.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Hynrei, U Blei u la ong ha nga, ‘Men ym tei ka ïing ma me ïa ka kyrteng jong nga, naba me long u nongïapom, bad me la pynmih snam.’",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> La kumta ruh, U Trai, U Blei ki Israel, u la jied ïa nga na baroh ka ïing u kpa jong nga ban long u syiem halor ki Israel junom: naba u la jied ïa u Judah ban long u nongïalam; bad ha ka ïing u Judah, ka ïing u kpa jong nga; bad napdeng ki khun u kpa jong nga u la sngewbha ïa nga ban pynlong syiem ïa nga halor ki Israel baroh:",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> bad na ki khun shynrang jong nga baroh, (naba U Trai u la ai ïa nga shibun ki khun shynrang,) u la jied ïa u Solomon u khun jong nga ban shong halor ka khet ka hima U Trai halor ki Israel.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad u la ong ha nga, ‘U Solomon u khun jong me, ma u, un tei ïa ka ïing jong nga bad ïa ki phyllaw jong nga: naba nga la jied ïa u ban long u khun jong nga, bad ma nga ngan long u kpa jong u.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad ngan pynskhem ïa ka hima jong u ha la ka rta, lada u ïaineh ban leh ïa ki hukum jong nga bad ïa ki jingbishar jong nga, kumba ha kane ka sngi.’",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Mynta, namar kata, ha khmat ki Israel baroh, u paidlang jong U Trai, bad ha kaba ïohsngew U Blei jong ngi, to sumar bad to wad ïa ki hukum baroh jong U Trai U Blei jong phi: ba phi lah ban ïoh ïa kane ka ri ka babha, bad ban pynsah ïa ka kum ka jingïoh pateng ha ki khun jong phi hadien jong phi ha la ka rta.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> “Bad ma me, ko Solomon u khun jong nga, to ithuh ïa U Blei jong u kpa jong me, bad shakri ïa u da ka dohnud bajanai bad da ka jingmut ba mon sngewbha: naba U Trai u ïit ïa ki dohnud baroh, bad u sngewthuh ïa ki jingpyrkhat baroh jong ki jingmut: lada men wad ïa u, men shem ïa u; hynrei, lada men kyntait ïa u, u ruh un kyntait noh ïa me ha la ka rta.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> To sumar te; naba U Trai u la jied ïa me ban tei ka ïing ïa ka jaka kyntang: to long u bakhlaiñ, bad to leh ïa ka.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ynda kumta, u Dabid u la ai ha u Solomon u khun jong u, ïa ka nuksa jong ka batsha jong ka templ, bad ka jong ki ïing jong ka, bad ka jong ki ïing jingkynshew jong ka, bad ka jong ki kamra ba shaneng jong ka, bad ka jong ki kamra ba shapoh jong ka, bad ka jong ka ïing jong ka jingtap-isynei:",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> bad ïa ka nuksa jong kita baroh ba u la ïoh da U Mynsiem, ïa ki phyllaw ka ïing U Trai, bad ïa ki kamra baroh sawdong, ïa ki ïing jingkynshew jong ka ïing U Blei, bad ïa ki ïing jingkynshew ïa kiei kiei ki bakyntang:",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> ïa ki jingïakylliang ruh jong ki lyngdoh bad ki Lebi, bad ïa ki kam baroh kiba dei ha ka jingshakri ka ïing U Trai, bad ïa ki khiew ki pliang baroh kiba dei ha ka kam hapoh ka ïing U Trai:",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> ïa ka ksiar da ka jingthew ïa ki pliang ksiar, ïa ki pliang baroh kiba ha ka jaid baroh ka kam; ka rupa ïa ki pliang rupa baroh da ka jingthew, ïa ki pliang baroh kiba ha ka jaid baroh ka kam:",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> da ka jingthew ruh ïa ki dieng pynïeng sharak ksiar, bad ïa ki sharak jong ki, ka ksiar, da ka jingthew ïa kawei kawei ka dieng pynïeng sharak bad ïa ki sharak jong ka: bad ïa ki dieng pynïeng sharak rupa, ka rupa da ka jingthew ïa kawei kawei ka dieng pynïeng sharak bad ïa ki sharak jong ka, katba kum ka jingpyndonkam ïa kawei kawei ka dieng pynïeng sharak:",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> bad ka ksiar da ka jingthew ïa ki miej ki 'pu pyni, ïa kawei kawei ka miej; bad ka rupa ïa ki miej rupa;",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> bad ki proh doh, bad ki pliang, bad ki khuri, da ka ksiar banylla: bad ïa ki bol ksiar da ka jingthew ïa kawei kawei ka bol; bad ïa ki bol rupa da ka jingthew ïa kawei kawei ka bol;",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> bad ïa ka duwan ka jingiwbih ka ksiar ba la phrang da ka jingthew: bad ka ksiar ïa ka nuksa jong ka kali, ki Kherub keiñ, kiba la pyiar la ki thapniang, bad kiba tap ïa ka synduk ka jutang U Trai.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> “Ïa kane baroh,” ong u Dabid, “la pynsngewthuh ïa nga ha ka jingthoh na ka kti U Trai, ïa ki kam baroh jong kane ka nuksa.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad u Dabid u la ong ha u Solomon u khun jong u, “To long uba skhem bad uba shlur, bad to leh ïa ka: wat sheptieng, lymne khaw-eit: naba U Trai U Blei, U Blei jong nga keiñ, u long lem bad me; un ym iehnoh ïa me, lymne kyntait ïa me, tad ynda la pyndep ïa ki kam baroh kiba dei ha ka jingshakri ka ïing U Trai.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad ha khmih, don ki jingïakylliang ki lyngdoh bad ki Lebi, ïa ka jingshakri baroh jong ka ïing U Blei: bad un don lem bad me ha kano kano ka kam baroh uwei uwei baroh u briew uba mon sngewbha, uba don ka jingnang na ka bynta kano kano ka jingshakri; ki kaptan ruh bad ki paidbah baroh kin long shitylli hapoh ka hukum jong me.”"
		},
		"29": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ynda kumta, u Dabid syiem u la ong ha u paidbah baroh, “U Solomon u khun jong nga, ïa uba U Blei u la jied tang ïa u hi, u long uba dang samla, bad uba dang lung, te ka kam ka long kaba khraw: naba ka ïingbah kam long ïa u briew, hynrei, ïa U Trai U Blei.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te nga la khreh katba lah la ka bor na ka bynta ka ïing U Blei jong nga, ka ksiar ïa kiei kiei kiba da ka ksiar, bad ka rupa ïa kiei kiei kiba da ka rupa, bad ka rnong ïa kiei kiei kiba da ka rnong, u nar ïa kiei kiei kiba da u nar, bad ka dieng ïa kiei kiei kiba da ka dieng; ki maw Oniks, bad ki maw ban buh, ki maw ban pynitynnad, bad kiba bun rong, bad ki kynja mawkordor baroh, bad ki mawleiñ byllai.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Nalor kata ruh, namar ba nga la buh la ka jingieit sha ka ïing U Blei jong nga, haba nga don ka jingkynshew la ka jong, ka ksiar bad ka rupa, nga ai ïa ka ha ka ïing U Blei jong nga, nalor baroh ba nga la taïar na ka bynta ka ïing bakhuid;",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> haduh lai hajar talent ksiar, ka ksiar Ophir, bad hynñiew hajar talent rupa ba la phrang, ban suit ïa ki kynroh jong ki ïing da ki:",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> ka ksiar ïa kiei kiei kiba da ka ksiar, bad ka rupa ïa kiei kiei kiba da ka rupa, bad ïa ki kynja kam baroh ïa kiba yn trei da ki kti ki nongtrei bastad buit. Uei te u ban aiti sngewbha ban pynkyntang ïa lade ha kane ka sngi sha U Trai?”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ynda kumta, ki rangbah ki ïing ki kpa, bad ki rangbah jong ki jaid Israel, bad ki kaptan ki hajar bad ki jong ki shispah, lem bad ki nongsynshar halor ka kam u syiem, ki la ai sngewbha;",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> bad ki la ai na ka bynta ka kam ka ïing U Blei, ka ksiar san hajar talent bad shiphew hajar darik, bad ka rupa shiphew hajar talent, bad ka rnong khatphra hajar talent, bad u nar shispah hajar talent.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad kita ha kiba la shem ki mawkordor ki la ai ïa ki ha ki jingkynshew ka ïing U Trai, ha ka kti u Jehiel jaid Gershon.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te ki paidbah ki la ïalehkmen, namar ba ki la ainguh sngewbha, naba da ka dohnud ba-beit ki la ainguh sngewbha ha U Trai: bad u Dabid u syiem ruh u la leh kmen da ka jingkmen bakhraw.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Namar kata, u Dabid u la kyrkhu ïa U Trai ha khmat u paidlang baroh: bad u Dabid u la ong, “Long ba la kyrkhu ïa me, A Trai, U Blei jong u Israel u kpa jong ngi, junom la junom.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ka jong me, A Trai, long ka jingkhraw, bad ka bor, bad ka burom, bad ka jinglah, bad ka jinglong syiem: naba baroh kaba don ha bneng bad ha ka khyndew ka long ka jong me; ka jong me long ka hima, A Trai, bad la kyntiew ïa me kum u khlieh halor baroh.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad ka spah bad ka burom ki wan na me, bad me synshar halor baroh; bad ha ka kti jong me long ka bor bad ka jingskhem; bad ha ka kti jong me ka long ban pynkhraw, bad ban ai bor ha baroh.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Mynta, namar kata, A U Blei jong ngi, ngi nguh ïa me, bad ngi ïaroh ïa ka kyrteng ba-donburom jong me.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> “Hynrei, nga, nga long uei, bad ki briew jong nga ki long aïu, ba kumne ngin lah ban ainguh da ka mon sngewbha haduh katne? Naba kiei kiei baroh ki wan na me, bad na ka jong me hi ngi la ai ïa me.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Naba ngi long ki nongwei ha khmat jong me, bad ki sohshnong, kumba ki kpa jong ngi baroh ki la long: ki sngi jong ngi ha ka khyndew ki long kum ka syrngiew, bad ym don jingshong neh.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> A Trai U Blei jong ngi, kane ka jingkynshew baroh ïa kaba ngi la khreh ban tei ïa me ka ïing na ka bynta ka kyrteng bakhuid jong me ka wan na ka kti jong me, bad baroh ka long ka jong me hi.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Nga tip ruh, A U Blei jong nga, ba me tynjuh ïa ka dohnud, bad ba me sngewbha ha ka jingbeit. Ma nga te, da la ka jingbeit ka dohnud nga la ainguh sngewbha ïa kine kiei kiei baroh: bad mynta nga la ïohi da ka jingkmen ïa ki briew jong me, kiba don mynta hangne, ba ki ainguh sngewbha ha me.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> A Trai, U Blei u Abraham, u Isaak, bad u Israel, ki kpa jong ngi, to ri ïa kane junom ha ka jingpyrkhat ki jingmut ka dohnud ki briew jong me, bad pynkhreh ïa ka dohnud jong ki sha me:",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> bad to ai ha u Solomon u khun jong nga ka dohnud bajanai, ban sumar ïa ki hukum jong me, ïa ki jingphla jong me, bad ïa ki aiñ jong me, bad ban leh ïa kine kiei kiei baroh, bad ban tei ïa ka ïingbah, kaba nga la taïar na ka bynta jong ka.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad u Dabid u la ong ha u paidlang baroh, “Mynta to kyrkhu ïa U Trai U Blei jong phi.” Te u paidlang baroh u la kyrkhu ïa U Trai, uba U Blei ki kpa jong ki, bad ki la dem la ki khlieh, bad ki la mane ïa U Trai, bad ïa u syiem.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad ki la kñia ki jingkñia ha U Trai, bad ki la ainguh ki jingainguh thang ha U Trai, kum lashai hadien kata ka sngi, haduh shi hajar ki masi lyngraw, shi hajar ki langbrot shynrang, bad shi hajar ki khun langbrot, lem bad ki jingainguh dih jong ki, bad ki jingkñia kyrhai na ka bynta ki Israel baroh;",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> bad ki la ïabam ki la ïadih ha khmat U Trai ha kata ka sngi da ka jingsngewbha bakhraw. Bad ki la thung syiem ïa u Solomon u khun u Dabid ka ba-ar sien pat, bad ki la pynsleh ïa u sha U Trai ban long u nongïalam, bad ïa u Sadok ban long u lyngdoh.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Ynda kumta, u Solomon u la shong halor ka khet jong U Trai kum u syiem ha ka jaka u Dabid, u kpa jong u, bad u la man bha; bad ki Israel baroh ki la kohnguh ïa u.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Bad ki rangbah baroh, bad ki riewkhraw bor, bad ki khun shynrang u syiem Dabid baroh ruh, ki la pyndem ïa lade ha u Solomon u syiem.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bad U Trai u la pynkhraw ïa u Solomon shikatdei eh ha khmat ki Israel baroh, bad u la ai ha u kum kata ka jinglong syiem kaba ym shym la long ha uno uno u syiem uba ha shuwa jong u ha Israel.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Te u Dabid u khun u Jesse u la synshar halor ki Israel baroh.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Bad ka por ba u la synshar halor ki Israel ka la long sawphew snem; hynñiew snem u la synshar ha Hebron, bad laiphew lai snem u la synshar ha Jerusalem.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Te u la ïap haba u la tymmen bha, ba la dap da ki sngi, ka spah, bad ka burom: bad u Solomon u khun jong u, u la synshar ha ka jaka jong u.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Te ki kam jong u Dabid u syiem, ki banyngkong bad ki bakhatduh, ha khmih, la thoh ïa ki ha Ka Jingïathuhkhana u Samuel u nongïohi, bad ha Ka Jingïathuhkhana u Nathan u nongïathuhlypa, bad ha Ka Jingïathuhkhana u Gad u nongïohi;",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> lem bad ka jingsynshar jong u baroh bad ka bor jong u, bad ki por kiba la pynleit ha u, bad ha ki Israel, bad ha ki hima baroh jong kita ki ri."
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;